(486, 137, 'KP-56', 'obs', 'The Hygiene awareness sessions were not conducted in the catchment area of water supply scheme.', 'It is planned and decided that the mentioned session will be organized after the completion of tendering process/initiation of physical work and after completion of schemes the said session would be conducted. This would be useful for the community.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-12-09', 'Acheived', '2023-09-12', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(485, 137, 'KP-56', 'obs', 'It was observed that pretesting of water quality was not conducted.', 'It has been agreed with the contractor that he will ensure the pretest before initiation and post water testing after completion of the scheme to ensure the water quality before and after the DWSS.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-12-09', 'Acheived', '2023-09-12', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(484, 137, 'KP-56', 'obs', 'The need assessment was not conducted with the support of village committee as per scheme identification criteria. The committee was formed 2-3 months after the assessment conducted by SRSP staff. However, a community focal point who was later chosen committee president, was with the technical team at the time of assessment.', 'The process for DWSS starts with initial assessments involving community activists, and looking into social, technical, and financial feasibilities. Once the schemes are feasible then community mobilization process starts and followed by other important elements like formation of village committees, documentation and trainings sessions etc. This process is adopted to avoid community expectations in advance so that if the scheme doesn', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '0000-00-00', 'Acheived', '2023-09-13', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(483, 137, 'KP-56', 'obs', 'The Village committee was not fully informed about feedback and response mechanism. The FRM should be part of the agenda of every meeting/activity in the community.', 'FRM has been included in the agenda as a mandatory part of every training, meeting, and activities of DEC-II and HUM-II. community\'s feedback is important in all respect.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '0000-00-00', 'Acheived', '2023-09-13', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
