(459, 128, 'Sindh-74', 'act', 'Benefactrices were not fully aware about daily wages', 'Establish a clear and accessible system for sharing this information with beneficiaries to ensure transparency and empower them with the knowledge they need. ', 'District Coordi', '2018-09-20', 'Acheived', '2023-09-18', 'Beneficiaries were made orient on wages and activity details', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
