(457, 128, 'Sindh-74', 'act', 'The village committee was formed and all the documentation was present but it seems village committee was not fully involved in identification of schemes. ', 'To enhance the village committee\'s involvement in scheme identification, it\'s essential to address the existing awareness gap. Organize interactive sessions for committee members, and laborers, focusing on scheme details and the committee\'s specific role.', 'District Coordi', '2018-09-20', 'Acheived', '2023-09-18', 'MEAL team had debriefing session with IP and set a plan to have meeting with VC and keep them involved in future activities.', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(456, 120, 'KP-53', 'obs', 'Training was conducted by SCI Education Coordinator as Training Facilitator and CP Case Worker of SRSP as co facilitator though SRSP has the education coordinator available to facilitate the training.', 'SRSP will engage the education coordinator in training activities instead of CP Case Worker. Proper engagement of education coordinator will be more helpful in conducting the training as well as providing facilitation and support in group work activities, collecting feedback, answering the queries of the participants and training follow up.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-11-30', 'Acheived', '0000-00-00', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(454, 120, 'KP-53', 'obs', 'One of the participants shared that ', 'MEAL manager communicated the feedback of the participant to the SRSP staff at the training venue who informed that ', 'Dawood, CP Case', '2023-08-29', 'Acheived', '2023-08-29', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(455, 120, 'KP-53', 'obs', 'The training started one hour late as some of the participants had to come from very far area while traveling for about 4 hours.', 'Reference to this aspect of the finding, for onward and currently ,hotel accomodation has been made mandatory for participant coming form far flung area.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-09-22', 'Acheived', '2023-09-22', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(453, 120, 'KP-53', 'act', 'Due to cultural sensitivity, the female teachers requested for separate training session with females instead of combined session with male teachers.', 'The subject facilitation has been agreed for female participatnt and  we have planned Teachers and CP training like for male tecaher venue will be any hotel while for female venue will be any GGPS.\nRecently, teachers and CPC training for GGPS Ushu and women community of village Ushu was separately arranged. the same would be followed in coming trainings/activities.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-10-19', 'Acheived', '2023-10-19', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(452, 120, 'KP-53', 'act', 'FRM explained by MEAL Manager it was not part of the training agenda', 'FRM session is mandatory in each activity/training. FRM banner is displayed, explained and community feedback and response is recorded through FRM forms. So as the same process was adopted during this training but it was missed to be mention in the agenda. After this finding each training under the project DEC II and HUM II FRM has been made the mandatory session in the agenda of each training, and activity.', 'Sayyed Sajjad, ', '2023-09-28', 'Acheived', '2023-09-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(450, 119, 'KP-52', 'act', 'Feedback response mechanism was not part of training agenda. Upon probing, the students were not familiar with FRM.', 'FRM will be included in the agenda and the facilitator will be advised to provide the orientation about FRM in the coming sessions.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-28', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(451, 119, 'KP-52', 'obs', 'After the session, the facilitator asked a few children to go down and bring the refreshment packs from the driver. It may be noted that the distance was about one KM down the hill by foot.   The driver could have been asked to bring the refreshment packs to the school, but the SRSP staff shared that the community does not allow any male to enter the girls\' school and the children are familiar with the pathway and can easily bring the packs. This practice is against the child protection/safeguarding policy and the staff need to be instructed to avoid such practice in future.', 'The team will be advised to avoid such issues in the future. The children will not be asked to do anything except participation in the session. Its compliance will be ensured.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-28', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(449, 119, 'KP-52', 'act', 'The training manual was available with the facilitator, but handouts were not available for the participants. Furthermore, the copy of the agenda was not distributed among the children.', 'Colored copy of handouts and agendas will be translated to URDU and will be provided to the participants in the coming sessions.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-28', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(448, 118, 'KP-51', 'obs', 'One of the participants shared that the process of providing the per diem amount by SRSP is not feasible. They provide us the payment after 2-3 weeks of the training through a bank or Easypaisa account. We request that the per diem amount should be paid in cash on the last day of training.', 'The participants will be asked to confirm the availability of an active bank/Easypaisa account before transferring the per diem amount. Normally it takes two weeks to transfer the payment due to procedural issues. The participants will be informed accordingly.\nAs per SoPs the cash payment could not be provided.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-28', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(447, 117, 'KP-50', 'obs', 'It was informed by the patient, while conducting exit interview, that she was provided the treatment including medicines, but her children were not provided any treatment. Meanwhile the SO (Mr. Shaukat) informed that we have not enough medicines so we can only provide the treatment to one member of the family.', 'To avoid stock out, the SRSP health team will be advised to take more stock of medicines based on the average OPD of different diseases per day or based on daily consumption records of previous health camps to cater to the needs of more patients.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-31', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(446, 117, 'KP-50', 'act', 'Capacity of frontline workers of MHT was not assessed and not provided with required training.', 'Training of front-line health workers is planned from Sep 7th to Sep 15th, 2023.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-31', 'Acheived', '2023-08-28', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(445, 117, 'KP-50', 'act', 'The essential medicines and nutrition supplies were out of stock at nearly 1:30 pm. Majority of the patients were provided only one or two medicines after that. A few of the patients were not provided any medicines due to stocked out at the mobile health camp site.', 'To avoid stock out, the SRSP health team will be advised to take more stock of medicines based on the average OPD of different diseases per day or based on daily consumption records of previous health camps to cater to the needs of more patients.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '2023-08-31', 'Acheived', '2023-09-09', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
(444, 116, 'KP-49', 'obs', 'There was water seepage from the roof and walls/floor also needed minor repair. The WASH facilities were not functional. The water supply line was also damaged therefore water was not available in the school. The boundary wall of the school appear to be at risk of land sliding. The pathway need to be made safer for safe access to school by children of all ages.', 'The assessment of the school has already been conducted for rehabilitation work under DEC II. Most of the highlighted issues will be resolved after the completion of rehab work as the scope of work depends of availability of budget.', 'SRSP/Facilitato', '0000-00-00', 'Acheived', '0000-00-00', '', '', 'Usama Qayyum', '2023-12-11 19:00:00'),
