(13, 1, 49, '[\"168\"]', '[\"15\"]', '-	Sain Bux Shar -	Alam Khan Gopang -	Jam Khan Pahore -	Bux Khan Noonari -	Ali Gul Katohar --	Noor Muhammad Moorojo -	Faqeer Muhammad Bachal Dharejo -	Sono Shaikh -	Halepto Community  -	New Abad', '[\"144\",\"145\"]', '<p>HUM fund localization project is implementing in District Khairpur. The main theme of project is child protection integration to climate change. The partner is MRDO and working in union councils are Bugro and Shadi Shaheed in 10 targeted areas in district Khairpur. We There are three outputs of the project.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Output-1:</strong> Girls and Boys access safe spaces in community to enhance gender-equitable attitude and psychosocial wellbeing</p><p>The output one is covering the child protection activities, included establishment of safe of safe spaces, establishment of child protection committees and Child clubs and &nbsp;capacity building of CPCs and CCs, distribution of 1100 dignity kits.</p><p><strong>Output-2:</strong> Climate accountability of communities enhanced through localized eco-activism of girls and boys&nbsp;</p><p>The output one is covering the climate change activities, including 50 climate change sessions, distribution of 150 KG tool kit and KG activities and distribution of Bicycle to the school going girls, distribution of 3000 climate change booklets.</p><p><strong>Output-3:</strong> Localized accountability mechanisms strengthened for sustained gender inclusion and climate activism&nbsp;</p><p>The output one is covering the capacity building of partner staff, 5 coordination meetings with stakeholders and capacity building of stakeholders regarding child protection and climate change institutional development of project staff.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '2024-07-29 10:15:26', '2024-07-29 10:15:26'),
