(9, 'Complainant was further guided to submit the application to PPHI management and request them for compensation , because SCI supports PPHI in HR as per their proposed HR list which consists one M.O & one WMO in each health facility.', '2023-09-07', 114, 'Open', NULL, '2023-09-15 09:53:01', '2023-09-15 09:53:01'),
(10, 'Yesterday I had a meeting with Contractor M/S Karvan Buliders of the GPS Ayeen Ashoka. Mr. Usman Shah is the Site Supervisor for the said school while Mr. Nawab Syed is the Co Partner of the Company. They both visited the site before initiation for planning and construction. So, there is no subletting of the contract in the school. The SRSP and Contractor Team will ensure the presence of Staff and relevant documents on site along with staff list on each school.  \r\nBesides that, I had a detailed sessions with Company’s Owner and their Field Staff on SOPs for Safety, Safeguarding and SCI Policies along with SRSP Senior Engineer and Field Engineers. With this many issues relevant to such matters will be mitigated. I directed SRSP staff to involve the presence of SMC/PTC and CPC Committees and relevant stakeholders from start to finish as per QBs and scope of work.', '2023-09-13', 4, 'Open', NULL, '2023-09-18 05:39:15', '2023-09-18 05:39:15'),
