(550, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP. It was informed by SRSP that due to problem with CNIC data of some beneficiaries the whole batch of transaction was delayed by HBL Konnect. The revised data of CNICs was shared with the bank and the payment was received by all CFW beneficiaries except two. Later it was confirmed by MEAL team from the complainant that they have received the cash and were satisfied.', '2024-04-29', 1564, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:37:17', '2024-05-07 11:37:17'),
(551, 'It is a positive feedback of a beneficiary regarding communal handpumps.', '2024-04-18', 1587, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 11:38:25', '2024-05-07 11:38:25'),
(552, 'The SRSP Staff informed that the payment was delayed due to CNIC data of some beneficiaries due to which the bank delayed the batch transaction. However, on 24/04/2024 the payment has been received by all complainants. Later it was confirmed by MEAL team that the complainants have received their wage payment before 27th Apr 2024. The complaint was closed.', '2024-04-26', 1565, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:41:08', '2024-05-07 11:41:08'),
(553, 'SRSP staff informed that payment was delayed due to some CNIC data error of some beneficiaries. Therefore, the bank delayed the batch transaction. Later it was confirmed by the complainant that he received the payment on 25th April 2024. The complaint was closed.', '2024-04-26', 1566, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:44:03', '2024-05-07 11:44:03'),
(554, 'It is a positive feedback of communal handpump beneficiary.', '2024-04-19', 1588, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 11:47:05', '2024-05-07 11:47:05'),
(555, 'The complainant was told that SRSP/SCI do not provide books to any school, rather the books are provided by government. Therefore, he was advised to contact the government education department or school administration to get the books for the children. The complaint was closed after consultation with SRSP staff\'s feedback. The response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', '2024-04-30', 1567, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:47:30', '2024-05-07 11:47:30'),
(556, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP. He informed that rehab work was delayed due to rainfall and limited road access due to land sliding. However, the contractor has been asked to expedite the work. The rehab work will be completed before 20th May 2024 and quality of work will be reviewed by SCI and SRSP field engineer. The response was communicated by MEAL team to the caller, and he was satisfied. In case the rehab work is not completed by 20th May 2024 then complainant was requested to lodge the complaint again.', '2024-05-06', 1568, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:52:54', '2024-05-07 11:52:54'),
(557, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP and SCI field engineer. The SRSP staff informed that all the rectification work as per BOQs will be completed before 20th May 2024. The work was delayed due to bad weather. The roof leakage will be resolved. The water supply scheme has been initiated by the community with the technical support of SRSP field engineer. The complaint was closed after receiving satisfactory response from SRSP. The site will also be inspected by SCI Field Engineer.', '2024-05-07', 1569, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 11:58:35', '2024-05-07 11:58:35'),
(558, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP and SCI Field Engineer KP. The SRSP Staff informed that the work was delayed due to bad weather. The roof leakage will be resolved by the contractor and other rectification work as pointed out by the complainant will also be completed before 20th May 2024. The site is regularly visited by SRSP field engineer and SCI field Engineer to confirm and review the rehab work. The response was communicated to the complainant, and he was satisfied.', '2024-05-07', 1539, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:03:44', '2024-05-07 12:03:44'),
(559, 'It is a positive feedback of communal handpump beneficiary.', '2024-04-19', 1589, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 12:05:57', '2024-05-07 12:05:57'),
(560, 'The SRSP Staff informed that boundary wall of BHU Bahrian has been raised and protected by razor wire, while drainage water from labour room will be resolved during the rectification work before 20th May,2024. The complaint was closed based on satisfactory action taken by the partner.', '2024-05-06', 1538, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:08:24', '2024-05-07 12:08:24'),
(561, 'The complaint was shared with Area Director KP, Project Manager SRSP and SCI Field Engineer. It was informed by SRSP staff that field engineer of SRSP and SCI have visited the site and the contractor was advised to complete the identified rectification work before 20th May 2024. The rehab work is delayed due to bad weather and water seepage from the boundary wall. The SRSP field engineer will ensure all rehab work as per BOQ is completed which will be endorsed by SCI field engineer before 20th May 2024. The complaint was closed based on satisfactory action taken by the partner.', '2024-04-30', 1449, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:13:20', '2024-05-07 12:13:20'),
(562, 'It is a positive feedback of communal handpump beneficiary.', '2024-04-19', 1590, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 12:14:36', '2024-05-07 12:14:36'),
(563, 'The complaint was shared with senior provincial management of SCI, project manager SRSP and SCI field engineer. The SRSP staff informed that the payment was delayed due to CNIC data error of some CFW scheme beneficiaries. Therefore, the HBL bank could not transfer the payment as it was batch transaction. Later it was confirmed by SRSP staff and the complainant that the payment has been received by the complainant before 27th April 2024 and he was partially satisfied due to late payment. In future, SRSP has decided to transfer the cash through money order instead of bank transfer which takes quite a long time.', '2024-04-30', 1414, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:18:13', '2024-05-07 12:18:13'),
(564, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP after monitoring visit by MEAL team along with SRSP staff. It was informed by SRSP staff that contractor was already intimated to complete all the pending work as per quality based on BOQ. SRSP Field engineer will ensure that all rectification work is completed as per BOQ before 20th May 2024. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner.', '2024-04-30', 1537, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:22:58', '2024-05-07 12:22:58'),
(565, 'The complaint was shared with project manager SRSP who informed that payment was delayed due to some procedural formalities by the bank. The inconvenience is regretted. However, the training participants will receive their perdiam payment in next 10 days. Later it was confirmed by the partner staff that the payment is received by the training participants, and they were satisfied. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner.', '2024-04-29', 1521, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-07 12:28:25', '2024-05-07 12:28:25'),
(566, 'It is a positive feedback of a livestock grant beneficiary.', '2024-04-23', 1591, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 12:34:01', '2024-05-07 12:34:01'),
(567, 'It is a positive feedback of a shelter beneficiary.', '2024-04-25', 1592, 'Close', 5, '2024-05-07 12:42:07', '2024-05-07 12:42:07'),
(568, 'Complaint shared with project manager SRSP. He replied that payment of 33 beneficiaries could not be processed due to CNIC data error. The bank rejected the payment transaction due to invalid CNIC numbers. Therefore, revised list of beneficiaries has been shared with the Bank after cancellation process of the last 33 beneficiaries. The payment is in process and beneficiaries will receive the cash before 20th May 2024. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner and sharing response with the complainant.', '2024-05-07', 1410, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-08 03:37:22', '2024-05-08 03:37:22'),
(569, 'Project Manager SRSP responded that due to some CNIC data error around 33 beneficiaries could not timely receive the cash. The inconvenience is regretted. However, we have completed the cancelation procedure and shared the revised list with the bank for payment. The bank takes at least 5-6 days to process the payment. Therefore all 33 beneficiaries will receive their payment well before 20th May 2024. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner and same response was communicated to the complainant.', '2024-05-07', 1583, 'Close', 4, '2024-05-08 03:48:50', '2024-05-08 03:48:50');
