(767, 'A team was sent on 28, June-2024 to check the complaint. It was found that despite of the instructions given by the distribution team, not to split the kits, the Head Teacher had split the kits between enrolled and unenrolled children of pre-nursery. The kits were collected and provided to the entitled enrolled children. The head teacher was advised not to split kits, if she intends to provide kits to the nursery children so they must be enrolled prior kits provision. the matter has resolved.', '2024-06-28', 1741, 'Close', 4, '2024-08-05 05:34:15', '2024-08-05 05:34:15'),
(768, 'Project Manager SRSP responded that \"We checked with the school and 25 new children were enrolled. Learning and hygiene kits are available and will be provided on 8th, Aug-2024 including the new enrollment.\r\nWater supply problem has resolved through provision of pipe. there is smooth water supply to the school now.\"', '2024-07-02', 1733, 'Close', 4, '2024-08-05 05:38:02', '2024-08-05 05:38:02'),
(769, 'Nutrition assistant has been shifted to Govt LHV room, this has been resolved. The crowd is controlled by Female and Male Social Mobilizers in the HF. The matter has been resolved.', '2024-07-02', 1677, 'Close', 4, '2024-08-05 05:45:41', '2024-08-05 05:45:41'),
(770, 'The project manager SRSP responded on 25th June 2024 that \"A detailed meeting has been conducted with MO and other staff members of BHU Laikot pertaining to the complaint. Code of conduct and work place SoPs have been discussed with them. An explanation has been called and warning has been issued to the MO. He has assured no such event will take place in the future\". The complaint was closed based on the action taken.', '2024-06-25', 1732, 'Close', 4, '2024-08-05 06:27:38', '2024-08-05 06:27:38'),
