(59, '2023-08-23', '891-Feedback Form (8/2023) Sanghar/Hakeem Brohi ', 'Shahida sain bux ', 'Close', '4', '172', 'Shahdadpur', 'Lundo', 'Hakeem Brohi', '10', 'Zakir Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3081756850', 'During today\'s training, I learned new things that I was previously unaware of, and I\'m very satisfied. I\'m eager to apply this newfound knowledge to my vegetable fields. I\'ve already experiencing vegetation at my field now I will apply this knowledge . The facilitator has been effective in teaching, and I\'ve gained a lot from the experience.', '3', 'Positive feedback shared with FSL manager and efforts were appreciated.', '3 Days Training on Good Agricultural Practices & Kitchen Gardening', '1', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', '', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-28', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, 'SCI Staff thanked back beneficiary for the appreciation and assured beneficiary for the provision same quality work in upcoming events.', 11, '2023-09-11 05:28:51', 13, '2023-11-17 10:42:25', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
