(61, '2023-08-22', '893-Feedback Form (8/2023) Dadu/Wahi Pandhi', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', 'Johi', 'Wahi Pandhi', 'Wahi Pandhi', '10', 'Imtiaz Chandio', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Partner Staff', '03127461546', 'She told that she is a Nutrition Assistant at BHU Wahi Pandhi, since she has joined she is struggling with the challenge of over crowding at her corner. There is no support staff to control & manage the crowd due to which she could not properly manage the follow up cases & admissions. Therefore she requested to be provided a staff member to handle & manage the crowd as she could smoothly accomplish her routine tasks.', '3', '', 'Patient Exit Interview', '3', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Habib Akhtar', 'H&N Manager', NULL, '2023-08-23', NULL, '2023-09-04', 'Partially Satisfied', '', NULL, 'Nutrition assistant was told that there is staff on SCI panel which is given allowance, and it is already discussed and agreed with PPHI Management, so It PPHI who will decide whether to add more staff or not.', 11, '2023-09-11 05:28:51', 13, '2023-11-06 05:11:38', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
