(67, '2023-08-25', '910-Feedback (8/2023) Dadu/Sewo Jamali', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', 'Johi', 'Wahi Pandhi', 'Sewo Jamali', '10', 'Shamshad', 'No', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'She complainted that she has\'nt been paid the per diem of 3 Days Good  Agricultural Practices & Kitchen Gardening. As she was not informed about the training so that she could\'nt attend the first 2 days of the training, through other participants she came to know about the training & she attended the training on the third day but she is not been paid with per diem, so she requested to be paid as she was not informed properly & she attended the training on the last day.', '3', '', '3 Days Training on Good Agricultural Practices & Kitchen Gardening', '4', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Aliman shah', 'FSL Manager ', '', '2023-08-25', '', '2023-09-13', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, 'It was checked with NRSP team that why she wasn\'t informed prior this training, it was come to know that she was not available at house, went to city for some work, every beneficiary in the village was prior informed by VC President according to NRSP staff, and she was paid for days she attended the training.', 11, '2023-09-11 05:28:51', 0, '2023-11-29 05:25:31', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68, '2023-08-25', '911-Feedback (8/2023) Dadu/Chakar Rustamani', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', 'Johi', 'Wahi Pandhi', 'Chakar Rustamani', '10', 'Fazul Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03318360365', 'He said that he is thankful to be assisted for the agriculture purpose. Further he told that if he would\'nt assisted he could not be able to grow crop for current season.', '3', '', '3 Days Training on Good Agricultural Practices & Kitchen Gardening', '3', '', '3', 'No', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 11, '2023-09-11 05:28:51', 5, '2023-10-05 07:02:12', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
