(115, '2023-09-19', '62348-1-49/Utror', 'Saba Saeed', 'Select Option', '2', '49', '5', 'Kalam', 'Utror', 'Hum Fund', 'Laal Muhammad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03488997778', 'I am a head teacher of GPS Utror, our school was assessed by SRSP team for rehab work. I wanted to ask that, when the rehab work will start? as Utror is very cold area, snow begins to fall around the end of October. In our area, the cement does not work during the snowfall season. I just wanted to request you if you could please start the work by end of this month.', '1', 'the query forwarded for the response.', 'School Rehabilitation', '4', '', '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad, Abid Ur Rehman', 'Project Manager SRSP, WASH & Shelter Coordinator (', NULL, '2023-09-19', NULL, '2023-09-19', 'NA', NULL, 0, 'it was reconfirmed from the complainant, the Rehab work at GPS utror is going on.', 7, '2023-09-19 10:29:11', NULL, '2023-11-21 09:57:40', 7, '2023-09-19 10:31:52'),
