(89, '2023-08-04', '837-Hotline (8/2023) Dadu/Bugg\r\n', 'Asif Ali', 'Close', '4', '100', 'KN Shah', 'Burira', 'Bugg', '6', 'VC Member', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03462857188', 'One of the village committee members shared “One of the IP staff visited CFS and misbehaved with male facilitator and passed very unethical comments about female facilitator. We will not tolerate this & not interested to continue with CFS at our village. Please look into this matter', '1', 'After getting solid evidences and without an itermediary discours(with faciliator and VC member) incident was confirmed by CFS facilitator (male) that one of IP staff insulted him and behaved in un-ethical manner which threatened to an unfavourable situation and discontinuation of CFS in this village. However, he did not confirm female (CFS facilitator) related comments by IP staff.\nFurther Investigation is under process.', 'Child Friendly Space', '6', '24682', '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Datix', 'Reffered to datix ', NULL, '2023-08-04', NULL, '2023-08-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, 13, 'According to gender safeguarding specialist the case is under investigation and according to SCI_HR Whistleblowing Policy we have to ensure that the individual reporting a concern should not suffer any detrimental treatment as a consequence of reporting. this is communicated in writing with the partner NRSP from gender safeguarding department.', 1, '2023-09-13 04:35:53', NULL, '2023-11-29 05:20:13', 13, '2023-10-05 08:35:40'),
