(121, '2023-07-04', '791-Hotline numbers (7/2023) Swat/Kass madyen', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Kass madyen', '3', 'Faheem ul Islam', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03428972610', 'i visited to mobile health camp along with my wife and child (2 years). the doctore has prescribed my wife 2 mediciens. The staff has given the one me medicine from the clinic and for the other one they said that you will purchase it from market. my question is, if the mobile health camp offers free check up and medicine why the staff has asked me to purchase the other medicine from market?', '1', 'Syp Magnet formula cificeme and syp gunman formula sodium acid caitrat. this is mobile health camp patient. this patient have UTI(urinary tract infection). we gave cifixeme and sodium acid caitrat. we communicated the message to the patient to buy gunman syp from the outside because it is not available in the medicine list. The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'Mobile Health clinic ', '4', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-07-22', '', '2023-07-25', 'Satisfied', '', 3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
