(122, '2023-07-11', '792-Feedback Form (7/2023) Swat/Ossar', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Ossar', '3', 'Akbar Shah', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03449609944', 'Due to the earthquake, two walls of the schools damaged. there are cracks on the other walls of schools which needs repairment. the roof of class rooms and varanda is leaking. floor of the school also requires repair work. water supply line is damaged as well. there are only 2 classrooms in the school for 140 students. so we need to have one another class room and two washrooms for teachers and students.', '3', 'the points suggested by the respondant are already taken care of during school assessment for rehablitation work. Detailed BoQs were prepared by engineer. ', 'Temprory Learning Centre ', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-07-23', '', '2023-07-26', 'Satisfied', '', 3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(123, '2023-07-11', '793-Feedback Form (7/2023) Swat/Ossar', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Ossar', '3', 'Dost Muhammad', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'i attended the meeting with child protection committee. during the meeting the awareness about children\'s health, education and hygine was provided. it was asked to prohibit beating children at homes and schools. we got awareness about thr future of children. we will follow these points. all kinds of support will be given for the welfare of children. if needed we will refer the children to different organizations which can fulfil their needs for health, nutrition and eduction. at the end we are thankful to SRSP for establishing the children\'s cummittee and the plan to rehablitate the school.', '3', 'Positive feedback received and shared with partner staff', 'Temprory Learning Centre ', '1', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Project Manager SRSP', 'Accountability Officer', '', '2023-07-24', '', '2023-07-27', 'Satisfied', '', 3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(124, '2023-07-26', '794-Hotline (7/2023) Swat/Torwal', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Torwal', '3', 'Naveed', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'I visited to the Mobile Health Camp set up in our village, Torwal. i waited for my turn but the team had closed the camp for the lunch. right after that when i reached to them they informed me that their time for the mobile health camp has just ended up and they closed the camp at 2:30.  I wanted to know why the camp was closed at 2:30 if the advertised time on the banner is 5:00 PM.', '1', 'a focal point responded that, At 1:45, the team took a 30-minute lunch break. At 2:13, the clinic has resumed. There were no patients at the mobile health site from 3:17 to 3:47.Since morning, they had examined roughly 267 patients. A few medicines were running short after lunch, so they had to close the clinic at 3:47. The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'Mobile Health clinic ', '4', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-07-25', '', '2023-07-28', 'Satisfied', '', 3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(125, '2023-07-31', '795-Hotline (7/2023) Swat/Fateh Pur', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Fateh Pur', '3', 'Almas Khan', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'I attended the training TICC organized by Save the Children. We were only given PKR 1500 each day from your organization, which is insufficient. the other International organizations are giving a substantial amount in terms of perdiem to the training participants. also, the daily cost of transportation from my village to the training location is PKR 700. The perdiem amount we recieved spent on paying for the transportation and we have no saving from it. it is requested to please increase the amount of  perdiem.', '1', '1500 per day per person was allocated in budget. therefore the same amount was provided to all the teachers who attended the training. Since the perdiem was provided to the teachers to cover their travel cost therefore its not meant for saving. The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'Temprory Learning Centre ', '4', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-07-26', '', '2023-07-29', 'Satisfied', '', 3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(126, '2023-08-02', '808-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', 'Madyan', '', '', '3', 'Salahudin', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03432987268', 'I appreciate Save the Children for providing me with PKR 25,000 three months ago. I am a chef, and the flooding had a serious impact on both my home and my business. I would like to ask that, if it\'s possible, your organization reconstruct my home and shop so that I can resume my work.', '1', 'we responded to the caller that, provision for the reconstruction or rehabilitation of house or shop is beyond the scope of Save the Children. therefore, we cannot assist in the reconstruction of house or shop. The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'MPCA ', '3', '', '3', 'No', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '2023-07-30', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(127, '2023-08-02', '811-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/Aryani', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Balakot', 'Aryani', '3', 'Habib un Nabi', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03169055760', 'I am a government teacher in the GPS Aryani I School. Your organization established TLCs along with facilitator in the village when the flood caused damage. The TLC facilitator made the classroom a welcoming and attractive setting for the students, which increased their interest in going to school. In the month of June 2023, the contract of the TLC facilitator, got expired. There are just three teachers available to teach the 280 students at the TLC. The sixth grade for girls-only was also added in the TLC. Since it is quite difficult for us to adequately teach everyone. We kindly request you to provide us the TLC facilitator again.', '1', 'The focal point respondent that, since we have handed over the TLC to government, in June 2023. Therefore we cannot provide any further assistance. The copy of the signed handing over document is also there with the school staff which cleary mentioned that the organization will not provide any assistance after the mentioned time period.The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'Temprory Learning Centre ', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-02', '', '2023-07-31', 'Satisfied', '', -2, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(128, '2023-08-01', '815-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/Kas Bishigram', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Bishigram', 'Kas Bishigram', '3', 'Bahadur ', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03438864678', 'I\'m from the village of Bashigram. Flooding has destroyed our area\'s and the school\'s water supply system. If your company could help us fix the water supply system, it would be really appreciated.', '1', 'As per the partner response, we have completed the assessment of 8 targeted schemes under DEC II. there is no further provision of any additional scheme. this site was already visited by team, and it was not found feasible. the same response communicated to the caller, and he is satisfied.', 'Drinking water supply scheme', '3', '', '6', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-01', '', '2023-08-01', 'Satisfied', '', 0, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(129, '2023-08-03', '829-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/Ushu', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '', 'Ushu', '3', 'Khalid Ahmad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03475124956', 'I am on the mobile health clinic arranged in village chamgaray  with my wife and kids for a checkup. Since the morning, we have been waiting for the medical staff, but as of this moment (9:30 am), nobody is at the mobile clinic. In the medical camp, more patients are also waiting.', '1', 'As per the WMO response, the health team departed from office at 8:00 am. Approximately halfway through the journey, the vehicle developed an electrical fault. therefore, the team was unable to reach to the site on time.  however, some of the team members reached to the mobile health clinic at 9:35 am and the doctors with medicine supplies reached the site at 10:15 am. the health camp activities started afterwards. according to WMO some parents/ caregivers demand nutrition supplies for children without the prescription of the doctor. the MHT is trying to counsil the parents/caregivers that nutrition supplies are only for children suffering from malnutrition. the response has been communicated to caller and he is satisfied also he confirmed that the MHT has arrived and activities are resumed.', 'Mobile Health clinic ', '4', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Dr. Kashmala', 'WMO', '', '2023-08-03', '', '2023-08-02', 'Satisfied', '', -1, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(130, '2023-08-04', '830-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/Loi', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Behrain', 'Loi', '3', 'Bashir Ahmad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03459459624', 'I am a government teacher in the GPS Loi School. The tents provided SRSP has been damaged due to rainfall and thunderstorms. We kindly request you to provide us the new tents for the School.', '1', 'The focal point respondent that, since we have handed over the TLC to government, in June 2023. Therefore we cannot provide any further assistance. The copy of the signed handing over document is also there with the school staff which cleary mentioned that the organization will not provide any assistance after the mentioned time period.The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'Temprory Learning Centre ', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-04', '', '2023-08-03', 'Satisfied', '', -1, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(131, '2023-08-07', '853-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/old Mankiyal', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Mankiyal', 'old Mankiyal', '3', 'Nazia', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 Years ', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03143896658', 'I am a teacher of GGPS old Mankiyal. The SRSP conducted 6 days training for the teachers from 18th July 2023 to 23th July 2023. we were informed that we will get the TA with in a week but we did not recieve any amount till date.', '1', 'Qadeem Mankyal Teacher\'s pay order has been issued by the bank and she will receive it till tomorrow. our team has communicated the message to her and she is satisfied.', 'Teacher Training', '4', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-07', '', '2023-08-04', 'Satisfied', '', -3, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(132, '2023-08-07', '854-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/old Mankiyal', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Mankiyal', 'old Mankiyal', '3', 'Nazia', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 Years ', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03143896658', 'there is an open main hole in side the GGPS old Mankiyal which is dangarous for students. kindly fill the hole on urgent basis. secondly, we request you to provide the stationery for the school. ', '1', 'The partner team visited GGPS Qadeem Makiyal and had a meeting school management. the septic tank was properly coverd and precaution was displayed to avoid hazard/risk. it was discussed with the school management that civil work will be initiated in coming week and the hazard will be addressed permanently during school rehab work. School MGT will sensitise students on it. ', 'Rehablitation', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-07', '', '2023-08-05', 'Satisfied', '', -2, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(133, '2023-08-16', '859-Hotline (8/2023) Swat/Laikot', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Balakot', 'Laikot', '3', 'Mumtaz', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 Years ', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03149298955', 'I am a ex nazim of village Liakot. I visited the BHU Liakot for medical checkup, the doctor checked me and prescribed me a medicine. I received medicine from the BHU. however, I want to share that the medicine provided by your organization is not the quality medicine. it is not effective. i want you to check the quality of your medicine. Please arrange a call with your health experts with me so that i could inform them about the poor quality of the medicine being issued by your organization.', '1', 'The complainant was informed that there is not enough evidence to conclude that medicines provided at health facilities are low quality and not effective. However, we will see if we get more evidene from community about effectiveness of medicines then we will review the list of medicines and will replace those medicines.', 'Health Facility ', '4', '', '4', 'No', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '2023-08-06', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(134, '2023-08-22', '897-Feedback Form (8/2023) Swat/Kamar Shah', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Old Mankiyal', 'Kamar Shah', '3', 'w/o Umar Gul', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03163034850', 'Flooding has affected my home and my land. In the location where we currently reside, there is a water supply issue. there is not water tank, which need to store water for daily use. Furthermore, we frequently lack access to water for bathroom use. We are 20–25 households who have the same problem.  i request if your organization could help us in water provision.', '3', ' At the moment there is no scheme available. \nThe assessment of 8 Drinking Water supply Schemes under DEC-II have been idnetified and sent for tendering process after approval from SC Technical lead on WASH. However, this has noted if there is any further provision of DWSS then this will be assessed and accomodated.', 'water supply scheme', '3', '', '6', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-07', 'Satisfied', '', -17, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(135, '2023-08-19', '898-Hotline (8/2023) Swat /Shamtoo Guzargan', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyen', 'Shamtoo Guzargan', '', 'Abdul Qayyum', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03476504832', 'i received 25000 amount few months back from SRSP, i want to request if you can provide the amount again. furthermore, if you can please provide me any job so it will be highly appriciated', '1', 'the caller was informed that, we are not able to provide any job or further cash assistance. as we dont have budget for it.', 'MPCA', '3', '', '3', 'No', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '2023-08-08', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(136, '2023-08-23', '901-Feedback Form (8/2023) Swat/Dad Tarogay', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', 'Khwaza Khela', 'Shalpin', 'Dad Tarogay', '3', 'Noor ul Hadi', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'The process of providing the per diem amount by SRSP is not feasible. They provide us the payment after 2-3 weeks of the training through a bank or Easypaisa account. We request that the per diem amount should be paid in cash on the last day of training.', '3', 'The Partner responded that, Cash disbursement is not allowed as per finance rules. However, the process of payment through bank account or easypaisa account takes time due to bank procedures. The participants will be asked to confirm the availability of an active bank/Easypaisa account before transferring the per diem amount. Normally it takes two weeks to transfer the payment due to procedural issues. The participants will be informed accordingly.', 'CPC Training', '4', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-09', 'Satisfied', '', -15, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(137, '2023-08-24', '902-Feedback Form (8/2023) Swat/Chail', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Beshigram', 'Chail', '3', 'Shahi gulza', 'No', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'I arrived at the medical camp early in the morning with my two children. I waited for my turn for so long. I was registered by the staff members, but my children were not. I had a medical checkup and recieved the prescribed medicines by the pharmacy. However, if it\'s possible, please give my children an appointment with the doctor as well.', '3', 'the accountability officer, asked from the partner staff. they responded that, we have the shortage of medicine that\'s why we provide the checkup to only one of the family member. the accountability officer took the complainant\'s children towards medical doctor and provided them the medicine from pharmacy in the medical camp. furthermore,  She also suggested to the SRSP staff that all beneficiaries should receive a medical checkup.', 'Medical Health Camp', '5', '', '4', 'No', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '2023-08-10', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(138, '2023-08-24', '903-Feedback Form (8/2023) Swat/Chail', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Beshigram', 'Chail', '3', 'Rukhsana', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03453754109', 'I arrived at the medical camp at 8:00 am with my children. we got the medical checkup at 2:00 pm by medical doctor. Only the medication prescribed by me has been given to me by the pharmacy. the pharmacist didn\'t give my children their medicine. He told me that the medications are stocked out. I ask that since this camp is for the deserving members of the community, there should be plenty of medicine available so that everyone can receive their full medication. I belong to a poor family, hence i cannot afford to purchase these medications.', '3', 'the complaint was forwarded for the response.', 'Medical Health Camp', '5', NULL, '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-24', 'Satisfied', '', -13, 'the complainant was informed that, some medicines were stocked out earlier than expected due to a greater influx of patients. Therefore, some patients could not be entertained. our staff is also available at BHU Behrain. you can also visit there for free medical assistance. next time it will be ensured that there will be no stock out.', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 7, '2023-10-23 04:25:33', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(139, '2023-08-23', '904-Feedback Form (8/2023) Swat/Cham Shalpin', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', 'Khwaza Khela', 'Shalpin', 'Cham Shalpin', '3', 'Abdul Rauf', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03439425852', 'the payment we provide by the SRSP in terms of per diem is not sufficient for us. we came from the far flung areas and spend money on the rents. as per the high inflation, we would request for the increase the per diem amount and on time payment.', '3', 'the partner responded that, 1500 per day per person was allocated in budget. therefore the same amount was provided to all the participants who attended the training. Since the perdiem was provided to the participants to cover their travel cost therefore its not meant for saving. The same response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 'CPC Training', '4', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-12', 'Satisfied', '', -12, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(140, '2023-08-29', '905-hotline (8/2023) Swat/Dad Tarogay', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', 'Khwaza Khela', '', 'Dad Tarogay', '3', 'Amin ul Haq', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03493733432', 'I am a Child protection committee chairmain. we had recieved CPC training last week but we have not recieved the per diem amount till date. can you please expidate the process and provide us the amount.', '1', 'The Partner responded that, Cash disbursement is not allowed as per finance rules. However, the process of payment through bank account or easypaisa account takes time due to bank procedures. The participants will be asked to confirm the availability of an active bank/Easypaisa account before transferring the per diem amount. Normally it takes two weeks to transfer the payment due to procedural issues. The participants will be informed accordingly.', 'CPC Training', '4', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', '', '2023-08-30', '', '2023-08-13', 'Satisfied', '', -17, '', 11, '2023-09-19 17:39:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
