(191, '2023-07-25', '803-Feedback Form (7/2023) khairpur /Marecha Muhalla ', 'Shakila Memon ', 'Close', '4', '168', 'Kotdiji', 'Talpur Wada ', 'Marecha Muhalla ', '8', 'Heer Nand ', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '', 'The team visited our village for assessment of HHs for MPCA assistance, they did not assess our HHs despite the fact that we belong to minority. Our Mohallaha was ignored in MPCA ', '3', 'Case was jointly investigated by MEAL, Program & IP representatives. Team visited respective community & interacted with complainants. Following are the key points concluded by fact finding team. \n\n•	Mallah -Meghwar mohallah has around 150 HHs. IP team along with Village Committee, assessed 66 HHs including 44 from the minority community. \n•	60 HHs including 38 from the minority community were approved for the MPCA assistance.\n•	One approved case (Minority HH) has issue of incorrect CNIC which need to resolved. \n•	Allegation of ignoring minority HHs is baseless as 44 HHs were assessed & 38 cases were approved for assistance  \n•	Criteria (Exclusion/Inclusion) need to be re-shared with respective community.\n', 'MPCA ', '5', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager ', '', '2023-07-25', '', '2023-07-30', 'Satisfied ', '', 5, '', 11, '2023-09-21 11:25:57', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
