(210, '2023-08-10', '856-Hotline (8/2023) Khairpur/Ghulam Mustafa', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', 'Tharimirwah', 'Hindyari', 'Ghulam Mustafa', '10', 'Maqsood Ahmed ', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 Years ', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03058094486', 'A complaint received from Maqsood Ahmed he said I got my son vaccinated from PPHI BHU Hindyari a month ago, since my child\'s birth I get my son vaccinated (immunization vaccinations such as polio, and measles etc given at birth, and then at 2, 4 months, from this BHU) this time the vaccination has reacted badly and my son\'s skin is badly stuck to the bone, and he is in pain, I took my son to the BHU and asked them to check as after getting vaccinated from here my son is suffering from this pain, but they denied that this is not due to the reason you are mentioning neither we have first-aid right now to treat your son, and you also get your son checked from any other private Dr and if he confirms that this is due to this vaccination then we will see.\nI got my son checked from other senior doctor, Dr Waris Kubar, and he confirmed this as a reaction of vaccination and this will be resolved by an operation he also said the patient will feel an immediate burning pain, which can result in paralysis or neuropathy that does not always resolve, so I am really very worried now, and I am not financially that much stable to deal with this issue, so kindly look this matter also requesting you to help me and save my son\'s life.', '1', 'After receiving complaint , complainant was called along with his son to get checked in this regard DM along with Dr. Karam Abbas, District EPI Coordinator visited BHU plus Hindyari, met with Mr. Maqsood Ahmed and checked up the infant baby, reportedly the skin of the baby is badly stuck to the bone due to vaccination. During checkup following points have been observed. \nThe baby was physically fit and healthy. \nNo side effects of vaccination have been found. \nVaccination of the baby was done as per protocols. ', 'Vaccination', '5', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Habib Ahmed ', 'H&N Manager ', '', '2023-08-16', '', '2023-08-21', 'Satisfied ', '   ', 5, '', 11, '2023-09-21 11:25:57', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
