(431, '2022-10-28', '180-Feedback Form (10/2022) Swat/Mankyal', 'Sajid Khan', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Mankyal', 'Mankyal', '9', 'Sahib Gul', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0311-9156489', '\"My hosue is fully damaged and not included in the beneficiaries list of SRSP\"', '3', 'SRSP assessment team verified that his house was not fully damaged but partially damaged. He was not informed to visit the site and received relief items because on that occasion complete damage houses were informed and had to be facilitated. later, he was informed and facilitated on November 24, 2022 in the category of partially damaged house beneficiaries.', 'Food Aid Distribution', '4', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'MEAL Focal Person SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed with Delay', '2022-11-24', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(432, '2022-10-28', '181-Feedback Form (10/2022) Swat/Mankyal', 'Sajid Khan', 'Close', '2', '49', '9', 'Mankyal', 'Mankyal', '9', 'Abdullah', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0315-9495297', '\"Abdullah son of Shireen zada complained that his house was fully\ndamaged but he did not receive (Food & NFI) package. Although his\nbrother Zaid Ullah received the (Food & NFI) package\". ', '3', 'Sherin Zada has two sons i.e .Zaidullah and Abdullah (the complaint).Both brothers live in separate houses. The 2022 flood damaged the elder brother Zaidullah house and thus he was issued a token for the provision of relief package. During assessment in October 2022 Abdullah (the complaint) took the assessment team to his brother house and claimed that the house belonges to him. The village council chairman, community along with the assessment team visited Abdullah house and found the house safe and sound. Thus he can\'t be facilitated because he doesn\'t fulfil the criteria of fully or partial damage house. The message has conveyed to the complainant that he doesn’t fulfil the criteria for relief items as his house is safe. he can\'t be provided with relief items.', 'Food Aid Distribution', '4', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'MEAL Focal Person SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed with Delay', '2022-11-15', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
