(434, '2022-10-28', '183-Feedback Form (10/2022) Swat/Mankyal', 'Sajid Khan', 'Close', '2', '49', '15', 'Mankyal', 'Mankyal', '9', 'Javed Khan', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0311-90860149', '“I would like to inform you that my house is also fully damaged, but I was not included by SRSP\nstaff for any kind of assistance like relief tent, household kit or food pack. I request you to include me for the assistance.”', '3', 'SRSP Staff accepted the feedback from complainant and was given assurance that SRSP staff will contact him in a few days to verify\n the status of his house. The complainant agreed to it and went back satisfactorily.  Later SRSP staff conducted assessment of the\ncomplainant after receiving feedback from the complainant. It was observed and also verified by nearby community that his house\n was partially damaged and not fully damaged by flood. Later he was included on the basis of partially damaged house and facilitated\non 24, Nov,2022 with food assistance accordingly.', 'Food Aid Distribution', '4', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'MEAL Focal Person SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed with Delay', '2022-11-24', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
