(707, '2023-02-11', '456-Email (2/2023) Swat/XX', 'Tehmina Javed', 'Close', '2', '49', '', 'XX', 'XX', '20', 'Hussain Akbar', '', 'Male', '', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', 'XX', 'Dear sir My House was damaged in 2022 flood and your staff have filled form for me. But now my name is not present in the list. Please accept my form and give me financial aid..My damage house pictures are attached.', '2', 'The Additional information is required to verify the assessment record. Mobile and CNIC number were mandatory which were not given. Since this information were not provided therefore no further action was taken.', 'Multi Purpose Cash Assistance (MPCA)', '3', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-02-11', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(708, '2023-02-17', '457-Email (2/2023) Swat/Damana', 'Tehmina Javed', 'Close', '2', '49', '', 'Tirat', 'Damana', '20', 'Mian Ijaz Ali', '', 'Male', '', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', 'XX', 'This is an appreciation email on behalf of the beneficiaries of the MCPA project of SRSP, funded by Save the Children at VC Tirat North Swat Kpk. As part of the project, a cash stipend of Rs. 25000 per family was distributed among 32 deserving beneficiaries of the vicinity. The money was given to orphans, widows, and disabled persons for clearing up their groceries’ and other children’s needs bills. The project was made successful, all thanks to the team members of SRSP on field, who worked tirelessly and dedicatedly. \nWhile we highly appreciate your current project, I would also like to bring to your notice the need for water and sanitation projects, women and children projects, disabled persons’ projects, and more in the area. Any future projects of such kinds will be highly and gratefully welcomed by our community. \nGod bless and anticipating future correspondence. \nYours sincerely \nMian Ijaz Ali &\nOn behalf of: Damana Welfare Committee VC Tirat North, Swat Kpk.\n', '2', 'Positive feedback shared with SRSP. ', 'Multi Purpose Cash Assistance (MPCA)', '1', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-02-17', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
