(937, '2023-06-05', '686-Hotline (6/2023) Swat/Tarrgay', 'Tehmina Javed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Madyan', 'Tarrgay', '20', 'Syed Waqas Ahmad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0347-8616337', 'we are very happy and thankful to Save the Children and SRSP for organizing health camp here in Tarrgay, Madyan.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with SRSP.', 'Medical Camp', '1', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-06-05', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(938, '2023-05-30', '687-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Laikot', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Balakot', 'Laikot', '20', 'Bakhroom', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0314-9721742/0313-98', 'My child was ill and i brought her to the medical facility, the doctor examined her thoroughly and the LHV has taken my history before going to the doctor. the LHV said the patient has some infection in her breast thats why she will be referred to a hospital. BHU closes at 1pm. Bakhrooma further said that Doctors are very supportive and competent, i came to BHU because i have been told that the doctor is a psychologist. ', '3', 'Positive feedback shared with SRSP.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '1', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-06-30', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(939, '2023-05-30', '688-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Aryanai', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Balakot', 'Aryanai', '20', 'Atta ul Haq', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0314-2220422', 'Our village has been affected badly by the recent floods in August 2022. it affected GPS Aryanai badly due to which education of the children has been severely Impacted. after that Save the Children established TLCs and education of the children has been started again and continued. for that we are very thankful to the organization and the facilitators in TLCs. Now we need washrooms facility, school bags and 4wing material for children. if there is any possibility please provide us the said materials. we will be very thankful to you.', '3', 'As per response from the partner, the rehabilitation work cannot be conducted in GPS Aryana I. as the school is situated near the river bank and flood prone area. the government did not allow rehablitiation work. therefore the school cannot be considered for rehab work. the same response was communicated to beneficiary and he was satisfied from the response.', 'TLC', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Satisfied', '2023-08-01', '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(940, '2023-05-30', '689-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Aryanai', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Balakot', 'Aryanai', '20', 'Group', 'Yes', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0316-9055760', 'We are very happy and satisfied with the establishment of TLC. due to floods our school boun4y wall and class class rooms have has been damaged severely which made us greatly disturbed. we have received learning kits provided by save the children and we are very thankful for that. Our school needs to be reconstructed. new class rooms and boundry wall need to be reconstructed. we dont hace washroom facility availble we practice open defecation. we need separate sports kits for boys and girls and school bags for new enrollments we also need 4wing books for all children. thank you', '3', 'As per response from the partner, the rehabilitation work cannot be conducted in GPS Aryana I. as the school is situated near the river bank and flood prone area. the government did not allow rehablitiation work. therefore the school cannot be considered for rehab work. the same response was communicated to beneficiary and he was satisfied from the response.', 'TLC', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(941, '2023-05-30', '690-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '', '', '20', 'Rehan Ullah', '', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '', 'BHU is not Flood Affected. Roof is not damaged. the boundry wall of BHU is intact. 2 WASh facilities are available.  two security guards are availbale for day and night duty. UPS and solar panel also available. we need Barbed wire for boundary walls to be protected from outsiders for safety of BHU supplies and equipments.', '3', 'Partner focal point responded that, rehablitation work will be conducted in BHU Behrain. the WASH facilities construction of new room, and installation of required partition will be part of the rehab work. if the barbed wire is recommended by government then it will be included in rehab work. the same response was communicated to beneficiary and he was satisfied from the response.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '3', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', '', '', NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(942, '2023-05-30', '691-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Bahrain', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Bahrain', 'Bahrain', '20', 'Mohammad Yasin', '', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'I brought my baby girl of one month. I got medicines for my sister and daughter of my brother. waited for one and half hour to receive treatmen due to large number of patients. I am satisfied with service delivery and free medications. i just paid Rs.10 for opd slip. I know in case of any cpmplaint I can call the specified phone number.', '3', 'Positive feedback shared with SRSP.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '1', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-06-30', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(943, '2023-05-29', '692-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Bahrain', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Bahrain', 'Bahrain', '20', 'Akbar Zeb', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0314-9293516', 'our people are very satisfied with the BHU services provided by Save teh children and SRSP. The SRSP staff has accomodation issues here in BHU. If possible please provide any tent or build separate medicine or pharmacy room. it will resolve many issues.', '3', 'As per the partner response, the rehabilitation work will include all necassary repair and maintanance of the BHU building. the same response was communicated to beneficiary and he was satisfied from the response.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '3', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(944, '2023-05-29', '693-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Bahrain', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Bahrain', 'Bahrain', '20', 'Khadija Jalil', '', 'Female', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'We have some issues, for example We dont have specified place for IYCF corner. we need multivitamins for pregnant and lectating women. We dont have space for screening, there are alot of patients for screening and all are satisfied but the main issue is space problem. please provide us separate and personal Nutrition Room.', '3', 'it was communicated by the partner, the space issue will be resolved as soon as WFP staff evacuates the BHU. moreover, further space problem will be resolved by adding some partition and reconstruction of one additional room during rehablitation work. \nlater, on 18th June 2023, it was shared by partner that space issue of nutritionist has been resolved. furthermore, the space for IYCF sessions and nutrition screening is also available at BHU Behrain.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '3', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(945, '2023-05-29', '694-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Zorr Kalay', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', 'Bahrain', 'Zorr Kalay', '20', 'Rabia', '', 'Female', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'We Receive alot of help from your team\'s arrival. my sister Sofia is mentally weak and her behavior has improved in first session provided by your organization for that we are very thank ful. we have seen a significant difference with the medicines and treatment provided by your organization.', '3', 'Positive feedback shared with SRSP.', 'Medical Camp- Static (BHU)', '1', '', '4', 'Yes', '', 'Syed Muhammad Sajjad', 'Project Coordinator SRSP', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-06-29', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(946, '2023-05-09', '695-Feedback Form (5/2023) Swat/Dad Tarogay', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '6', 'Shalpine', 'Dad Tarogay', '20', '', '', 'Male', '', '', 'Save the Children staff', '', 'The tents were partially damaged by snowfall in December 2022. Steel elbows and joints were broken but later it was fixed with temporary arrangement of wooden supports. The TLC may not be safe for children with wooden supports.            Since the elbows and joints were broken and alternate similar parts were not available in the market, therefore the broken parts were repaired, and some were replaced by making new from local wielders. To protect the tents from further damage, wooden supports were installed for additional safety of tents. However, the wooden supports/pillars will be replaced with steel frame pillars.\nIn future, it is recommended that customized tents should be made with steel pillars in the centre as the current tents were lacking that essential pillar in the centre. The vendour may be asked to provide some additional elbows and joints to be replaced in case of such emergency. Secondly the winterized school tents should be provided for establishing TLC or CFS in future to avoid water seepage due to rain or snowfall.\nWooden Pillars have been replaced with steel frame pillars.', '3', '', 'TLC- GPS Dad Tarogay', '6', '', '2', 'Yes', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-05-25', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(947, '2023-05-29', '696-Hotline  (5/2023) Chaman/Landi Karez', 'Tehmina Javed', 'Close', '3', '170', '1', 'Purana Chaman', 'Landi Karez', '', 'Abdul Ghaffar Achakzai', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Non-beneficiary', '0316-8139265', 'The level of education in our area specially girls education is equivalent to non-existent. there is extreme poverty here and there is lack of employment opportunities. It would be greatly appreciated if your organization could facilitate the arrangement of schooling for the children and could provide school bags and shoes for these poor children in our area. your support in this regard would be highly appreciated. this area is very poor and deprived, and there is a great need for education here. you team can visit this place and assess it. I request you to forward my message to your seniors and donors if possible to fulfil our needs if possible. Thank you.', '1', 'Request for Assistance shared with relevant person', '', '3', '', '2', 'Yes', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
