(970, '2023-06-22', '719-Feedback Form (6/2023) Thatta/Jatti Camp ', 'Shahida Sain Bux ', 'Close', '4', '174', '27', 'Kann Malik ', 'Jatti Camp ', '20', 'Muhammad ', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', '', 'Direct Beneficiary', '', 'We have been here for three days now, and we have been receiving support from the government. We were already happy with the assistance provided by them, and now we are even more delighted that you have come here to facilitate us. The main challenge we have been facing is the scarcity of food and water, and your provision of water assistance has been incredibly helpful. I am grateful for your help, and my children are also thrilled to receive these specially provided biscuits. Thank you so much for your care.', '3', 'Positive feedback was shared with repective team ', 'Emergency Response ', '1', '', '3', 'Yes', '', 'Naveed Sultan ', 'Ops Team Lead ', '', NULL, 'Closed Timely', '2023-06-22', 'Satisfied', '', NULL, '', 1, '2023-09-26 14:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
