(1035, '2023-10-12', '1034-1697971007', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Sahib Dino Shar', '10', 'Afsana', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03483240022', 'I participated in 3-day livestock training, I was told that on last day of training I will be provided with training stipend, but it was not provided.', '1', 'Query shared with the relevant person to address, response awaiting.', 'Livestock training', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-10-12', NULL, '2023-10-20', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'IP was asked with the reference of this complaint, it was told by IP that, on the last due to reasons it wasn\'t easy to disburse cash, so disbursed with delay of 2 days, due cash was given to all the trainees.', 13, '2023-10-22 05:54:16', NULL, '2023-11-07 09:12:24', NULL, NULL),
(1036, '2023-10-17', '1035-1698035446', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Sahib Dino Shar', '10', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3483240022', 'Complaint received via hotline, according to the complainant” NRSP Project Coordinator Tashkeel Abbas has reproved for launching complaint of delayed payment of livestock training Infront of community, which was completely humiliating for me also this has lessened my confidence for future to launch any complaint again”.', '1', 'Complaint shared with the concerned department to better address this query.', 'Livestock training', '5', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-10-17', NULL, '2023-10-31', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SCI team settled down the matter between beneficiary and PC IP, after listening to both parties it was come to know that there was a misunderstanding due to which complainant exchanged arguments with IP PC and resultantly took it as misbehavior, later both were guided well, and issue was resolved.', 13, '2023-10-22 23:43:27', 13, '2023-11-28 07:17:14', NULL, NULL),
(1037, '2023-10-20', '1035-1698035208', 'Maira Ansari', 'Close', '4', '100', '8', '93', 'Dadu', '6', 'Kamran Hyder', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Partner Staff', '03113632778', 'Thank you for inviting me to the NRSP and SCI child protection training. it is a valuable initiative for our society, creating awareness among people. I gained a lot of knowledge from this training.', '3', 'Positive feedback shared with concerned lead and appreciated their sincere efforts.', 'Training of Government official on child protection, mental health and psychosocial support, safe identification and referral conflict mitigation', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2023-10-20', NULL, '2023-10-23', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SCI Team thanked back beneficiary and recognized for positive feedback, also assured same work in the future.', 16, '2023-10-22 23:55:20', NULL, '2023-11-06 01:15:58', NULL, NULL),
(1038, '2023-10-16', '1036-1698036235', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '100', '38', '91', 'BHU Kolachi', '3', 'Mukhtiar', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'A complaint received via hotline from BHU Kolachi fostering to grievances according to the complainant “My wife was 9 months pregnant, she was going through recurrent pains (birth pangs), I took her to the BHU Kolachi to get her checked, whilst she asked Dr (FMO) to check her Dr misbehaved with her and  asked her to not to disturb her and come after a week as you still have time for accouchement (however 9 months already completed), she was suffering from parturition so I took her to nearby private maternity home, there Dr did some tests and discovered that her childbirth was expected 10 days prior to today’s diagnosis as there is swelling shown in the womb and immediate delivery was suggested, I am wondering if I haven’t took my wife to the private hospital she along with her fetus could have faced destructive harm”.', '1', 'Complaint shared with relevant department to further investigate and address the concerns, hence response awaiting.', 'Health Facility', '5', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Habib Akhtar', 'H&N Manager', NULL, '2023-10-17', NULL, '2023-10-26', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'A meeting was conducted with PPHI Staff and complainant, grudges were noted and patient was given enough empathy by the Dr, however duty Dr said, may be there was any miscommunication, we suggested her to go home you still have some time for child birth, according to her condition and she misunderstood it, however we still apologize for issues she faced.', 13, '2023-10-23 00:23:26', 1, '2023-11-16 08:17:07', NULL, NULL),
(1039, '2023-10-18', '1038-1698038876', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '92', 'Maqsodo Rind', '10', 'Ghulam Sakina', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03443723387', 'A complaint received via hotline prevailed upon as dissatisfaction towards activities, by a female MPCA beneficiary she said” I was on cotton picking (wasn’t informed prior to the distribution) a distant relative informed me about the distribution while I was in the cotton-fiber harvesting, I immediately rushed towards distribution point and asked the distributor to handover me my kit but he said all kits are distributed and there isn’t any other kit left to give you, in spite the fact that I am MPCA beneficiary”.', '1', 'Complaint shared with the concerned department to address the query and resolve the issue, awaiting response.', 'Hygiene Kit Distribution (MPCA)', '4', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinator', NULL, '2023-10-18', NULL, '2023-10-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'After checking with NRSP team it was come to know that distribution team tried to call her on her provided contact number, but it was not responding so she remained unaware of distribution, however she was provided her kit within 2 days on her doorsteps.', 13, '2023-10-23 00:42:57', NULL, '2023-11-29 05:57:38', NULL, NULL),
(1040, '2023-10-17', '1039-1698040353', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '39', '88', 'Bachal Khan', '3', 'Irshad Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03033952353', 'A complaint received via hotline from BHU Nara, complainant says \"his son has got a dog bite, but Dr is not checking him, providing unnecessary excuses and asking to get it checked by staff or just wait, my son isn\'t feeling well so help me\".', '1', 'Complaint shared with relevant head to address and resolve the query asap.', 'Health Facility', '4', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Habib Akhtar', 'H&N Manager', NULL, '2023-10-17', NULL, '2023-10-17', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Complaint was immediately shared with district PPHI staff to attend the patient as in SCI children and their well-being is very important, patient was checked and immediately given treatment (vaccination).', 13, '2023-10-23 01:01:58', NULL, '2023-10-25 05:09:37', NULL, NULL),
(1041, '2023-10-19', '1040-1698044574', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '36', '87', 'BHU Kolab Jeal', '12', 'Dr Rabia', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03229132127', 'In charge FMO said that there is no provision of toilets for male and females in this BHU, female patients and caregivers usually use labor room toilets which is not appropriate all the time, so we request for separate toilets.', '1', 'Feedback shared with the relevant lead to address the raised concern and resolve it.', 'Health Facility', '3', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Habib Akhtar', 'H&N Manager', NULL, '2023-10-20', NULL, '2023-10-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SCI has currently no provision for this request however PPHI can do that. A de-brief meeting was held with PPHI senior staff, according to him, we are working on rehabilitating the facilities so soon will work on this request.', 13, '2023-10-23 02:26:37', NULL, '2023-11-17 10:04:46', NULL, NULL),
(1042, '2023-10-19', '1041-1698046005', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '36', '87', 'BHU Kolab Jeal', '12', 'Reema', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'Female patient complaining about the non-provision of nutrition supplements, she said she is on contraception and bleeds a good deal, feels so weak and sick, I requested Dr for supplements, she didn\'t suggest anything rather providing iron tablets.', '3', 'Complaint shared with concerned department lead to take action and investigate if needed to resolve this feedback.', 'Health Facility', '4', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Habib Akhtar', 'H&N Manager', NULL, '2023-10-20', NULL, '2023-10-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Meeting with PPHI staff was conducted and asked the reasons for this complaint, Dr told that contraception method is provided on patient\'s choice, and we also share with them the sufferings being faced by that method, in addition to this we give them iron supplements, however nutrition supplements are for PLW.\r\nPatient was further guided by Dr accordingly.', 13, '2023-10-23 02:42:30', NULL, '2023-11-17 09:57:32', NULL, NULL),
