(1050, '2023-10-24', '1049-1698211408', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Mehar Khan Dasti', '10', 'Shahid Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3231358893', 'A complaint received via hotline from a CFW beneficiary he said “I worked for 12 days first, and then after a gape of few days\' work started for 12 more days, I am a daily wages based meson, and my (my family’s survival) is based on my daily wage income, and in the wait of this stipend I suffered a lot as there is no other income other than this, and since last 25 days I haven’t gone to porterage which has caused starvation in my family, and now I am so disappointed with the work you are doing”.', '1', 'Complaint shared with the FSL Manager to address the query and resolve the concerns, response awaiting.', 'Hygiene Kit Distribution (MPCA)', '5', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-10-24', NULL, '2023-10-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Due to system and compliance formalities, disbursement got late, however cash is disbursed now, and SCI apologizes for this delay.', 13, '2023-10-25 00:28:12', 13, '2023-10-31 05:44:45', NULL, NULL),
(1051, '2023-10-24', '1050-1698212169', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Khan Rind', '10', 'Imtiaz Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3452304326', 'A complaint received via hotline, it states” I received the hygiene kit distributed by SCI and I found some items missing in it (1. Clorine tablets 2. Nail Cutter 3. Towel) I managed to check the kits of others to confirm either items missing, or this is the only package given to me, resultantly, I come to know items are missing not only in mine but also in few others’ too, so please check and provide me all items as provided to others”.', '1', 'Complaint shared with WASH Coordinator to address the query, awaiting response.', 'Hygiene Kit Distribution (MPCA)', '5', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinator', NULL, '2023-10-24', NULL, '2023-10-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SCI Team conducted physical counting and verification of remaining hygiene kit’ items in all three districts, along with IP and noted that No missing items reported from any of the district and all items found in accordance with approved specs and quantity given in PO. Quality of items also found satisfactory and uniform. So, it seems that missing items issue is happening during transportation of kits to field, load/unload, as some of kits packing found damaged or rotten. For future distribution now onward IP is advised to display the list of hygiene items at each distribution point and ensure that all beneficiaries have been oriented about the number of items in local language and confirmation of receiving of all items as per list before beneficiaries leave the site.', 13, '2023-10-25 00:42:50', 13, '2023-11-20 08:33:52', NULL, NULL),
(1053, '2023-10-31', '1051-1698739146', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '92', 'Abdul Jabbar', '10', 'Sakina', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03452524065', 'A call received via hotline falling in the category of “Positive feedback” caller states “ I along with my family am grateful for the assistance provided by SCI (MPCA Cash and Hygiene Kit in hunger fund project), my sister in-law’s wedding date was fixed, however we didn’t have much to manage for her wedding in terms of wedding gifts for her, so on this foremost time we received assistance which has helped a lot and we acknowledge sincere efforts of SCI for unprivileged people like us”.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with the FSL Manager and efforts were appreciated.', 'MPCA (Additional beneficiary)', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-10-31', NULL, '2023-10-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'We SCI team inwardly acknowledge the positive feedback and will ensure same work spirit in the future.', 13, '2023-10-31 03:03:03', NULL, '2023-10-31 05:47:36', NULL, NULL),
(1054, '2023-10-20', '1053-1698739905', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '7', '40', 'Dital', '10', 'Zaibul', 'No', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'She said that she is very happy to receive this hygiene kit as it contains all the items which are in their daily consumption & also too expensive to afford them.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Distribution of Hygiene Kits to the MPCA beneficiaries', '1', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinator Sindh', NULL, '2023-10-31', NULL, '2023-10-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Senior WASH Coordinator is motivated on receiving thankful messages from the beneficiaries.', 5, '2023-10-31 03:37:05', NULL, '2023-10-31 03:58:04', NULL, NULL),
