(1069, '2023-11-06', '1069-1699267129', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '22', 'Aryanai', '9', 'Nagina', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3476564676', 'I am from the village of Aryanai. last month, the SRSP team visited villages Damana and Kalagram for the assessment. they formed a village committee for the above-mentioned villages and filled out the form of their community members. \r\nThe SRSP team did not visit our village although we all are flood affected. however, 4-5 families from our village were called to village Damana through the village chairman for assessment. we wanted to know why the team did not assess us or include us in the kitchen gardening scheme.', '1', 'the complaint referred for the response.', 'Conditional Cash Grant', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Ejaz Shah', 'MEAL Manager', NULL, '2023-11-06', NULL, '2023-11-27', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The Partner responded that, \"The mentioned two beneficiaries were included by village committees of daman and kalagram, living in the proximity. However, there was no further slots available, therefore further assessments for 1,000 CCGs were stopped.\"', 7, '2023-11-06 10:55:53', 7, '2023-12-11 07:06:43', NULL, NULL),
