(1135, '2023-11-22', '1135-1700641792', 'Sanam Altaf', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '92', 'Khan Jo goth', '10', 'Qalb Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03431981628', 'A complaint received via hotline from village-Khan jo goth, UC-Maqsoodo Rind, Tehsil-Shahdadpur, District-Sanghar, according to complainant” I am working under the scheme (repairing street) of cash-for-work which is considered as a bolstering of social safety nets and is intended to alleviate the strain of ongoing economic crisis in our village, but unfortunately nobody is supporting me in this street repairing work despite being selected beneficiaries for CFW in this second cycle, its my 3rd day and I only come to work, I ask my fellow workers but nobody is taking interest and now I am also fad up with this, in 1st cycle workers did the same, nobody was regular but received full payment of 12-days, even didn’t complete the scheme in 1st cycle, so I request you to please look after this matter. However, I shared this matter with NRSP team as well but didn’t receive any productive response, I have videos from last 3 days, which illustrates, I am only working on the site, but payment will be probably received by all workers.”', '1', 'As stated by provincial MEAL Manager, its category has updated from 5 to Category 4 with note  from him that initial statement seems cat 5 but upon initial fact finding we found that there is nothing backing serious part of compliant. Therefore, it was not handled as cat 5 and not reported on Datix. ', 'Cash for Work', '5', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-11-22', NULL, '2023-12-27', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'After receiving it was investigated and found that the complainant and other villagers completed the second cycle, and IP\'s technical team visited the place and discovered that the job was not up to set measurement, so they allocated some more work to be performed within time, and they were given two days of