(1164, '2023-10-12', '1164-1701684463', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Jaindo Rind', '10', 'Dr. Salma', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Partner Staff', '3269956955', 'Due to the current high patient flow, I am requesting assistance as it is challenging to allocate sufficient time to each patient. If possible, I would appreciate support, and there is also a need for MHM kits in the labor ward or any other hygiene-related items.', '3', 'Feedback shared & referred to the relevant department for better address to this request.', 'BHU visit', '3', NULL, '4', 'No', NULL, 'Dr. Habib Akhter', 'H & N Manager', NULL, '2023-12-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 10:17:49', 8, '2023-12-18 06:27:06', NULL, NULL),
(1165, '2023-11-09', '1165-1701685114', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Lal Bux rind', '10', 'Bashir', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3073187403', 'This informative session provided detailed insights into livestock, including the most common animal diseases and preventive measures to safeguard animals from diseases. The training clarified many aspects for me, and I appreciate the effort in arranging this wonderful session. Thank you so much for the valuable knowledge shared.', '3', NULL, 'Livestock Training', '1', NULL, '3', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 10:29:11', 8, '2023-12-07 05:50:22', NULL, NULL),
(1166, '2023-11-09', '1166-1701686001', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Lal Bux Rind', '10', 'Muhammad Hassan', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3089455076', 'This training has been highly informative and has dispelled some misconceptions I had about domestic animal diseases and vaccinations. It has provided me with valuable insights into proper vaccines and preventive measures for animals. I appreciate being a part of this training. Thank you so much for the knowledge shared.', '3', NULL, 'Three Day livestock Training', '1', NULL, '3', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 10:38:38', 8, '2023-12-07 05:54:28', NULL, NULL),
(1167, '2023-10-17', '1167-1701686352', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Khan Rind', '10', 'Mohan Lal', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3461370760', 'I\'m delighted to have received the hygiene kit. It\'s my first time participating in such work, and I feel fortunate to be selected as an MPCA. Unfortunately, I arrived late as I didn\'t receive information from NRSP about the distribution. Nonetheless, I am very happy and grateful. Thank you so much.', '3', NULL, 'Hygiene Kits Distribution', '1', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 10:52:17', 8, '2023-12-07 05:53:01', NULL, NULL),
(1168, '2023-10-17', '1168-1701687214', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Khan Rind', '10', 'Khalida', 'No', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0', 'I am delighted to have received this hygiene kit, and I also participated in the hygiene training. The training provided valuable insights into personal hygiene and MHM, and I learned new things. Thank you very much to arrange this type of training and provide kits for us.', '3', NULL, 'Hygiene kits distribution', '1', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 11:01:00', 8, '2023-12-07 05:49:45', NULL, NULL),
(1169, '2023-10-23', '1169-1701687695', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Khan Rind', '10', 'Salamt Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3072733495', 'I\'m thrilled to receive this kit, but I would like to understand the criteria for selection. My brother did not receive this assistance, and we are keen to gain a comprehensive understanding of the project and the selection process. Could you please provide more information on how individuals are chosen for these kits?', '3', 'Positive feedback and request for information was shared with relevant head.', 'Distribution of hygiene kits', '2', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinotr Sindh', NULL, '2023-12-19', NULL, NULL, 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-04 11:07:03', 8, '2024-01-12 04:43:16', NULL, NULL),
