(1171, '2023-11-09', '1171-1701750149', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Ghazi Khan Lashari', '10', 'Nasreen', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3033410126', 'I reside in the village of Ghazi Khan Lashari, but we belong to the Brohi community, situated slightly away from the Lashari community. While our village is considered part of the Lasharis, there is limited interaction between our Brohi community and theirs, even on special occasions. I kindly request the provision of latrines for our Brohi community, as both latrines constructed earlier were placed in the Lashari community. Additionally, we also require hand pumps.', '3', 'Feedback shared with WASH coordinator to better understand the request for assistance.', 'WASH schemes', '3', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinotr Sindh', NULL, '2023-12-19', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-05 04:56:56', 8, '2024-01-12 04:34:59', NULL, NULL),
