(1175, '2023-11-04', '1174-1701753398', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Jaindo Rind', '10', 'Imam Bux', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '3002259762', 'I would like to bring to your attention that in our village, Jaindo Rind, there is a suitable source of sweet drinking water located just a short distance away from us. I am earnestly requesting the provision of lead handpump to facilitate access to this water source. I have previously communicated this request to NRSP, emphasizing the need for lead handpumps. I am reiterating the same request, seeking your support in fulfilling this essential requirement.', '3', 'Feedback shared with the relevant head to better resolve the query.', 'WASH schemes verification', '3', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinotr Sindh', NULL, '2023-12-19', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-05 05:28:03', 8, '2024-01-10 04:57:38', NULL, NULL),
(1176, '2023-11-24', '1176-1701754366', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Moula Bux Chhutto', '10', 'Abdul Hameed', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3023094373', 'Our village consists of a total of 50 houses, and unfortunately, we lack any reliable source of safe drinking water. I earnestly request the installation of lead handpumps in our village to address this pressing need. I have observed that your organization has provided latrines in other villages, and I am curious why our village has not been selected for this assistance. Once again, I am requesting the provision of latrines, as open defecation is a prevalent issue in our village. Kindly take necessary measures to address both the water source and latrine needs in our community.', '3', 'Request for assistance shared with the relevant department to better resolve the query.', 'PDMs', '3', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, 'Muhammad Fazil', 'Senior WASH Coordinotr Sindh', NULL, '2023-12-19', NULL, NULL, 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-05 05:41:55', 8, '2024-01-10 04:48:13', NULL, NULL),
