(1228, '2023-12-06', '1227-1702289607', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Lal Bux Rind', '10', 'Javaid Hussain', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03412175061', 'The Save the Children organization is making a positive impact in my village. I am aware of various activities undertaken by Save the Children, such as cash-for-work initiatives, cash payouts, informative sessions, and training programs. Currently, they are also providing handpumps and latrines for our village. I understand that the organization conducts water quality tests before installing handpumps, which is commendable. This effort ensures that we are protected from various waterborne diseases.', '3', NULL, 'Verification of WASH schemes', '1', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-11 10:21:23', 8, '2023-12-12 10:26:06', NULL, NULL),
(1229, '2023-12-06', '1229-1702290244', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Sathi Khan Rind', '10', 'Khuda Bux', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3200027250', 'The toilet supplied by your organization has been beneficial. I can now conveniently wash my hands using the provided wash basin. Thank you very much for providing us with these toilets.', '3', NULL, 'Verfiication of WASH schemes at community  level', '1', NULL, '6', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-11 10:30:12', 8, '2023-12-12 10:24:49', NULL, NULL),
(1230, '2023-12-02', '1226-1702289184', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '28', 'Darmar', '9', 'xxx', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03348304959', 'I want to express my concerns regarding the poor quality of ongoing rehabilitation work at GGPS Darmar. In classroom flooring, the required material is not being used. We are not satisfied with the work. We request your technical experts for a thorough inspection of the rehab work be conducted at your earliest convenience.', '4', 'complaint forwarded for the response', 'School rehab', '5', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abid Rehman', 'Shelter and WASH Coordinator', NULL, '2023-12-11', NULL, '2023-12-14', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'As per the Shelter & WASH coordinator\'s response, \"I visited the said school (GGPS Darmar Shahgram). I inspected the quality of the Flooring of two classrooms where PCC was done. The PCC was as per BOQ, and workmanship is also good against the mentioned complaint. The materials placed on site were also good.\r\nHowever, besides the rehabilitation work, one new latrine construction is in progress. It is observed that the quality of work was substandard, and it was directly sent with observations to SRSP PM and technical team for compliance and report. It was also suggested for technical reasons to dismantle it and reconstruct it as per Drawings/BOQs/specifications. They will update me regarding further development to make sure all quality standards are followed.', 7, '2023-12-11 10:32:43', NULL, '2023-12-22 05:58:17', NULL, NULL),
(1231, '2023-12-11', '1231-1702293099', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '85', 'Goth Behram Khan', '5', 'Saddam Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03471316432', 'I belong to a poor family, last week your team visited our village and filled the forms for assistance. I want to request kindly add my name in the list as well.', '1', 'Please follow up with the complaint as per given details. Thanks', '2', '3', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Shazia Gul', 'Accountability Officer', NULL, '2023-12-11', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with the program team, and they conveyed that accommodating all beneficiaries is not feasible due to fund limitations. However, they have recorded the beneficiary\'s name and village for future reference. If an opportunity arises in the future, the program team expressed their commitment to providing support to the mentioned beneficiaries.', 28, '2023-12-11 11:28:02', NULL, '2024-02-13 10:40:38', NULL, NULL),
(1232, '2023-12-06', '1232-1702373899', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Rajpar Gothh', '10', 'Moto Mal', 'Yes', 'Male', 'Above 50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3443213163', 'As a laborer, I often finish work after 2 pm, and when I come to the BHU, doctors are not available at that time. If possible, I request a change in the BHU operating hours so that I can easily access healthcare services when the doctors are present.', '3', 'Request for assistance shared with relevant department.', 'BHU visit', '3', NULL, '4', 'No', NULL, 'Dr. Habib Akhter', 'H & N Manager', NULL, '2023-12-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-12 09:52:05', 8, '2023-12-18 06:35:42', NULL, NULL),
(1233, '2023-12-06', '1233-1702374822', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '17', '113', 'Berwari Village', '10', 'Asghar ali', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3282745491', 'I am grateful to always come to this BHU whenever I don\'t feel well today, I am here again to get medicines. I have a simple request, please provide a drinking water source as there is currently no proper access to drinking water.', '3', 'Positive feedback and request for assistance shared with relevant department to better address this situation.', 'BHU Visit', '3', NULL, '4', 'No', NULL, 'Dr. Habib Akhter', 'H & N Manager', NULL, '2023-12-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-12 10:02:17', 8, '2023-12-19 09:44:39', NULL, NULL),
(1234, '2023-12-06', '1234-1702375368', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '17', '113', 'Maqrani Gothh', '10', 'Shahbaz Ali', 'No', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0', 'I visited with my father, and I am delighted to have obtained medicine from here. I came from my village, and I always enjoy the experience of being here.', '3', NULL, 'BHU Naoabad', '1', NULL, '4', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-12 10:08:19', 8, '2023-12-12 10:28:07', NULL, NULL),
(1235, '2023-12-06', '1235-1702375864', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '17', '113', 'Village Lakka', '10', 'Keshi', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0', 'I would like to express my thanks. All the medicines here are provided free of charge. Whenever I come with my family, we always receive medication without any cost. Thank you.', '3', NULL, 'BHU visit', '1', NULL, '4', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1970-01-01', NULL, NULL, 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, '2023-12-12 10:20:27', 8, '2023-12-12 10:27:00', NULL, NULL),
