(1289, '2023-12-18', '1289-1702972141', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'Asharo Paty', '3', 'Habib', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0312769214', 'I am a village committee chairman. I have the following concerns:\r\n1.	The required water storage tank at the source is not constructed.\r\n2.	The required water connection lines were not laid in the community. \r\n3.	The local laborers engaged were not paid by the contractor yet.\r\nFurthermore, I want to request to expedite the work due to the chance of snowfall in the next few days.', '1', 'the complaint was shared for the response', 'Water Supply Scheme', '5', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abid Rehman', 'Shelter and WASH coordinator', NULL, '2023-12-18', NULL, '2023-12-19', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'As per the The site is under construction and is delayed due to site supervisor is on sick leave and hopefully will return to site in two or three days. The source tank and distribution lines are remaining with pipe purchased but not transported to site. With the Contractor\'s return all payments and the remaining work will be executed soon. \r\nthe response was communicate to the complainant and he is satisfied.', 7, '2023-12-19 07:53:52', NULL, '2023-12-22 06:03:24', NULL, NULL),
