(1292, '2023-12-15', '1292-1703050943', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Buggh', '6', 'Sardar', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03473150005', 'I am formally registering a complaint regarding a pressing issue that has been ongoing since August. My two colleagues and I serve as facilitators at CFS in Village Bugg. Despite our dedicated service, we have not received our expected salaries, causing considerable distress. It is disheartening that, to date, we have not received any payment. I kindly request urgent attention to this matter and seek clarity on when we can expect to receive our long-overdue payments.', '1', 'Complaint shared with relevant department to investigate and response to the query.', 'CFS', '5', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Fatima Shafique', 'Program Coordinator', NULL, '2023-12-18', NULL, '2023-12-25', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Complainant was informed that the salaries have been transferred to the accounts of all facilitators of the mentioned CFS despite the initial delay due to technical issues.', 8, '2023-12-20 06:29:47', NULL, '2024-01-16 06:25:42', NULL, NULL),
(1293, '2023-12-15', '1293-1703060178', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Bugg', '6', 'Rajab Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03443684282', 'My concerns and seek assistance regarding the ongoing assessment of the shelter program under your organization. Initially, my name was included in the early assessment, as communicated by NRSP. However, I was recently informed that my name did not make it to the final list, and NRSP indicated that my name was rejected. As a laborer supporting a family, this news has left me feeling helpless. I find it disappointed that my name is not only absent from the government shelter list but is also excluded from your organization\'s final list. I urgently request a review of my case and kindly ask for the inclusion of my name in the final list of beneficiaries.', '1', 'Complaint shared with the concerned department to better address this query.', 'Shelter', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator', NULL, '2023-12-20', NULL, '2023-12-18', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'After receiving complaint, concerns were shared with the technical team to investigate, it was come to know that he did not meet the criteria also beneficiary was guided about the selection criteria and SCI process to select beneficiaries, and he is already part SHBF Scheme.', 8, '2023-12-20 08:25:07', NULL, '2024-01-16 05:50:33', NULL, NULL),
(1294, '2023-12-18', '1294-1703061906', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '84', 'Village Rizk Khan Rind', '5', 'Ali Muhammad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03138588508', 'I work as a security guard at TLS I want to highlight a pressing issue regarding my salary. I joined in October, and up to now, I have not received my salary. This delay is causing significate financial hardship for me, particularly because I am the sole breadwinner for my family. I urgently request clarification on when I can expect to receive my salary.', '1', 'Complaint shared with relevant department to investigate the issue.', 'TLS', '5', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2023-12-19', NULL, '2024-01-03', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The issue was discussed with the program team and partner staff. According to their response, the matter has been resolved, and the security guard\'s salary has been successfully transferred to his account. They have also provided assurance that they will exercise increased diligence in the future to avoid any discrepancies regarding salaries.', 8, '2023-12-20 09:45:08', NULL, '2024-02-13 11:06:47', NULL, NULL),
(1295, '2023-12-18', '1295-1703067224', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Goth, Ali Nawaz Dasti', '10', 'Munwar Ali dasti', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0', 'I am reaching out to inform you that I have successfully recovered my 20,000 rupees, which were previously reported as being misappropriated for small business restoration. I had filed a complaint with the accountability officer, and I am pleased to share that I have now received the full amount of 20,000 rupees. Thank you so much for your assistance.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with relevant person.', 'Small business restoration', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Ali Aman shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2023-12-18', NULL, '2023-12-20', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SCI has expressed gratitude to the beneficiary and encouraged them to use cash for a specific purpose. It\'s great to acknowledge and thank beneficiaries for their involvement or support.', 8, '2023-12-20 10:45:24', 8, '2024-01-16 05:35:24', NULL, NULL),
