(1303, '2023-12-20', '1303-1703219511', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '19', 'Chanchary', '3', 'xxx', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', NULL, 'My son is a student of GPS chanchary. The SRSP team has distributed the learning and hygiene kits in the school. The other class fellows of my son has received the kits but my son did not receive anything. Now from yesterday my son is crying and saying that he will go to school only if he receives the same bag. I also went to school and discussed this matter with school administration. They informed me that we have received the limited number of items while the school strength is high. Therefore, we are unable to give the item to all the children. I wanted to ask on what criteria the kits were distributed, and my son is excluded from receiving the items?', '1', 'The complaint is forwarded for the response.', 'Distribution of learning kits', '5', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Rabia Rauf', 'Program Manager – Ops', NULL, '2023-12-21', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'we have been informed by Area Director that, the learning kits will be provided to all the children till class four after the vacation in march. the response was communicated to beneficiary and we informed him that in case his son did not receive the kit he can reach us again.', 7, '2023-12-22 04:34:59', NULL, '2024-02-13 11:26:14', NULL, NULL),
