(1308, '2023-12-18', '1308-1703226547', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '20', 'Torwal', '3', 'Fazl e Rabi', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03139842880', 'I am PST at GPS Torwal. the medical team of SRSP has visited our school for screening of the children for hearing and vision impairment. they checked a student in grade one and referred him to the Saidu Medical Hospital for further treatment pimple on his eye. the child with their parents visited the hospital today and the hospital staff referred them to the hospital in Peshawar. the child\'s family is poor and could not afford to visit Peshawar. I want to request that you help him in this regard.', '1', 'the request is forwarded for response.', 'screening of the children for hearing and vision impairment', '3', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager (SRSP)', NULL, '2023-12-22', NULL, '2024-01-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'the partner responded, \"The child was referred to SIMs Hospital Saidu Sharif to Dr Zeshan (Ophthalmologist), the Doctor checked his eye’s condition, discussed the case with other doctors, and was referred to Shifa Eye Trust Hospital Rawalpindi for eye surgery, on the follow up the parent said that they are very poor and unfamiliar with medical issues and hospitals, so they were reluctant to go to the hospital so far away.\r\n SRSP CP team developed linkages and came to know that there is one Doctor (Dr Yasir)of Mingora city in the mentioned hospital and also he does practices here on each second Saturday, on 10 February appointment was made for child checkup in Mingora and a parent will bring a child on Saturday (3 Feb-24) here to Mingora and then further the Doctor will suggest a good option for his surgery either here or there and in case of treatment in Shifa Eye Trust Hospital he also will facilitate them in the hospital.\"', 7, '2023-12-22 06:48:53', NULL, '2024-01-30 07:16:23', NULL, NULL),
