(1337, '2024-01-02', '1337-1705550364', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Sarfraz Lahsari', '10', 'Yar Muhammad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03480381246', 'I have not yet received my labor payment. I am concerned because your NGO is currently closed in our district. Could you please provide information on when we can expect to receive cash for our work?', '1', 'Request for information shared with relevant person.', 'Cash for work', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-01-18', NULL, '2024-01-25', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The Labor payment was dispersed, and the beneficiary received the first and second cycle of his labor payment.', 8, '2024-01-18 04:06:34', NULL, '2024-01-25 06:04:40', NULL, NULL),
(1338, '2024-01-08', '1338-1705550910', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Bugg', '6', 'Sajid Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3433257642', 'Initially, my name was included in the assessment list, and I\'ve maintained regular communication with the NRSP team, who assured me of my selection for shelter assistance. I carefully followed their instructions, specifically not registering my house for the government housing scheme or applying for other grants, as they warned that such actions could result in automatic removal from the shelter assistance list. I was shocked to learn last Friday that my name has been dropped, and I am no longer part of the shelter assistance. This news has left me in a state of despair, especially considering the loss of my house during the 2022 flood. Additionally, I am now facing the added challenge of being excluded from government housing schemes.  As I am poor and do not have any other avenue for support, your assistance is crucial. The impact of this decision directly affects my ability to rebuild and secure a place to live.', '1', 'Complain was shared with technical head for better understanding.', 'Shelter', '5', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-18', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint has been appropriately conveyed to our senior management team. The caller has been apprised that the immediate implementation of the requested intervention presents challenges, given that the current intervention sites have already been designated. Due to fund restrictions and limitations, we regret that we cannot accommodate all beneficiaries at this time. Nevertheless, please rest assured that your complaint will be taken into consideration for assessment in the future.', 8, '2024-01-18 05:11:15', 8, '2024-02-13 09:57:58', NULL, NULL),
(1339, '2024-01-04', '1339-1705559259', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '168', '14', '60', 'Photo khaskheli', '5', 'Ghulam Raza', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03022187551', 'Today was my first day as a facilitator at the TLS in village Photo Khan Khaskheli, having recently transferred from Village Kamal Wassan. Unfortunately, I encountered significant resistance from the community. The community members outright refused to accept me as their facilitator. They communicated their refusal explicitly and instructed me not to return to the village. Their main concern revolves around the security of adolescent girls, and they are adamant about not allowing me back into the village. I promptly reported this conflict to the TKF, but their response was not favourable. They simply advised me to continue with my job and adhere to the schedule. I am now at a loss as to how to proceed. The community\'s rejection is a significant obstacle, and I fear it may impact the children\'s participation in TLS and today only six students attended the TLS.', '1', 'Complain was shared with relevant person.', 'TLS', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-04', NULL, '2024-01-10', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Upon receiving Mr. Raza\'s grievance through the SCI hotline, our Partner TKF team promptly visited the TLS. A community dialogue was organized involving the TLS facilitator, community members, and the TKF team. Through consensus and mutual understanding achieved during the dialogue, the reported grievance has been successfully resolved.', 8, '2024-01-18 07:16:58', NULL, '2024-02-13 08:59:23', NULL, NULL),
(1340, '2024-01-05', '1340-1705573042', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Nabi bux Chhutto', '10', 'Ghulam Rasool', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'Your organization has done an excellent job, and as the president of the Village Committee in my community, I wanted to acknowledge the impactful work you\'ve done. Our village consists entirely of a poor community, and your organization\'s efforts have made a significant difference. Thank you for your outstanding work.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with relevant person.', 'Cash for work', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-01-18', NULL, '2024-01-25', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Positive response was shared with program team.', 8, '2024-01-18 10:22:42', NULL, '2024-01-25 05:46:12', NULL, NULL),
(1341, '2024-01-04', '1341-1705573391', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Jalal deen shar', '10', 'Ishaque ahmad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03000814068', 'I am a beneficiary of your livestock program, and although my name was finalized in your project, I have yet to receive the payment for the livestock. I am in dire need of cash, and it is concerning that I have not received any funds. Could you please provide information on when I can expect to receive my livestock grant?', '1', 'Request for information shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'Livestock', '2', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-01-18', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Concerned has been shared with the FLSA team. According to their response, after a certain period, the cash will be transferred to the beneficiaries\' accounts.', 8, '2024-01-18 11:18:33', NULL, '2024-02-13 08:40:59', NULL, NULL),
(1342, '2024-01-18', '1342-1705590680', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '83', 'Allah Abad', '5', 'Zaheer Ahmad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03408363182', 'Initially, my name was included in MPCA assistance but subsequently, it was rejected from the final list for MPCA cash assistance. This is deeply distressing for me as I am the sole breadwinner of my family, which includes my wife and three daughters. Currently, we are living in a tent due to the 2022 flood, which resulted in the loss of our house. Additionally, I am facing challenges in securing daily wage work. Unfortunately, I cannot leave my family alone to pursue alternative daily wage opportunities. Given the hardships I am already facing, learning that my name was not selected for MPCA assistance has added to my concerns. I urgently seek clarification on this matter and request your assistance in reviewing my case. Your attention to this issue is crucial for my family\'s well-being.', '1', 'Complain shared with relevant person for the better understanding and best resolution.', 'MPCA', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-18', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'We shared this complaint with the program team, and they assured that if the person meets the criteria, they will also be considered for assessment in future interventions. Unfortunately, due to limitations in funds, we regret that we cannot accommodate all beneficiaries at this time.', 8, '2024-01-18 15:31:30', NULL, '2024-02-13 11:14:08', NULL, NULL);
