(1357, '2024-01-19', '1357-1706156263', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '174', '30', '80', 'Faqeer Muhammad Rajero', '13', 'Asad Ali', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03032257416', 'I am student of 8th class at ALC during our free time, my friends and I love playing cricket. It would be amazing if we could get some cricket equipment to make our games even more enjoyable.', '1', 'Request for assistance shared with relevant person.', 'ALC', '3', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nighat Pathhan', 'Project Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-25', NULL, '2024-01-25', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Beneficiary was guided by SCI staff that there is no provision of game items such as cricket etc in this project, however anything comes information will be provided accordingly.', 8, '2024-01-25 04:24:10', NULL, '2024-02-13 08:45:55', NULL, NULL),
(1358, '2024-01-22', '1358-1706157425', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '83', 'Hazor bux umrani', '5', 'Muhammad Aslam', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03025051292', 'There used to be a school in our village the flood in 2022 caused extensive damage, disrupting everything, including the school. The education system has been severely affected, and despite our efforts, we have not been successful in rebuilding the damaged infrastructure. Regarding the school, I am requesting your assistance. Kindly provide us with support for the rehabilitation of the school or any other educational accessories such as copies, books, and bags. I came to know that your organization actively supports education, so if possible, please consider our school for your assistance. The situation is particularly concerning for girls and boys\' education, and any help you can provide would make a significant difference.', '1', 'Request for assistance shared with Relevant person for the better understanding.', 'TLS', '3', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-24', NULL, '2024-01-25', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with the program team, and their response indicates that they have effectively rehabilitated 27 schools and formed partnerships with the education department. Presently, they are unable to accommodate additional schools, but they are retaining the village and school names for potential future interventions.', 8, '2024-01-25 04:40:20', NULL, '2024-02-13 10:35:50', NULL, NULL),
(1359, '2024-01-24', '1359-1706157657', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '174', '30', '80', 'Village Shadyani', '13', 'Muhammad Rafique', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03032257416', 'I am a school teacher recently appointed at GBPS Yousif Shadyani. I have one request regarding the school, and I have also sent some pictures depicting the current condition of the school. I recently got your number and came to know that your organization is working on education. As a teacher, I am requesting your assistance because this school has been closed for the past 10 to 15 years and was reopened on January 8, 2024. Currently, 80 students are enrolled, with 47 girls and 34 boys. Unfortunately, there is no proper building for students, and we lack essential educational materials. We are compelled to conduct classes in an open ground, using makeshift arrangements. I am reaching out to you in the hope that you can aid in this matter. Please look at the provided pictures and consider doing something for these students. Approximately four villages\' students are studying here, and your support can make a significant difference in their education.', '1', 'Request for assistance shared with relevant person.', 'ALC', '3', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-24', NULL, '2024-01-26', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The request which has been duly communicated to our senior management team. The caller has been informed that implementing the requested intervention immediately may pose challenges, as the current intervention sites have already been selected. However, please be assured that your suggested school will be considered for assessment in the future.', 8, '2024-01-25 05:09:24', NULL, '2024-02-13 08:33:49', NULL, NULL),
(1360, '2024-01-23', '1360-1706160154', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '86', 'DC Chowk Muhalla Al Shehbaaz Colony', '5', 'Jameel Ahmad Mahar', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03463765776', 'Initially, I was grateful for the positive impact your organization was making in the educational sector. Both my daughters, aged between 5 to 8 years, were enrolled in TLS, and seemed to be enjoying their time there. However, our experience took an unfortunate turn during a recent distribution event for school bags and copies. During this distribution, only one of my daughters received the allocated items, while the other was left empty-handed. To make matters worse, when we approached the organization for the missing items, they not only refused but took the drastic step of expelling my daughter from TLS. The reason given for her expulsion was my written request seeking clarification on the discrepancy in the distribution of school bags and copies. This incident has left my family in disbelief. My younger daughter, now expelled, is struggling to comprehend the situation, and questioning her own eligibility for the TLS program. As a parent, I find this situation deeply disheartening, especially considering the organization\'s purported commitment to child protection and right. I kindly request a thorough investigation into this matter. It is crucial to understand the circumstances that led to the expulsion of my daughter and to ensure that such incidents do not recur.', '1', 'Referred to Datix', 'TLS', '6', '26868', '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sami Ullah Khan', 'Datix focal point', NULL, '2024-01-25', NULL, '2024-04-29', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Serious Compliant was reported to DATIX. An independent investigation committee was formed, and they investigated the case. Complaint was unsubstantiated.', 8, '2024-01-25 05:33:36', NULL, '2024-04-29 09:01:43', NULL, NULL),
(1361, '2024-01-26', '1361-1706261450', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '174', '23', '117', 'Rind Muhala', '13', 'Aswa Mehreen', 'Yes', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03262934933', 'I am a student currently in the 8th grade at ALC, and we are facing some challenges that I believe your support could help alleviate. We need essential educational supplies such as copies, books, school bags, storybooks and drawing items.  Additionally, there is a request for a water cooler to ensure that our basic needs are met.', '1', 'Request for assistance shared with Relevant person for the better \r\nunderstanding.', 'ALC', '3', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Farman Khan', 'Senior Program Manager Education/SHN', NULL, '2024-01-26', NULL, '2024-01-29', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Request was acknowledged and school bags was provided at the ALC along water cooler However, due to budget limitations, storybooks and extra stationery remain unavailable. We\'re exploring alternatives.', 8, '2024-01-26 09:40:44', NULL, '2024-02-13 07:36:02', NULL, NULL),
(1362, '2024-01-26', '1361-1706259810', 'Shazia Gull', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '83', 'City Dera Murad Jamali (Education Department)', '5', 'Syed Hizbullah Shah (Trainer)', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '3333368388', 'As a trainer i found the organization Save the children is good and working of education sector in focused areas in naseerabad and the training componant is so good the venue was aslso good.overall i found it good sector but after same time there is communication gap between trainer and team before training conduction it is necessary to convey the trainer about the agenda\'s and manual or out or ppts of session to ensure the conduction of good session of training.', '3', 'The positive feedback was shared.', '3-Days Training of NFE Facilitators at Naseerabad', '1', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abdur Razzaq Malik', 'Education Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-29', NULL, '2024-01-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The feedback was positive.', 14, '2024-01-26 10:14:28', 14, '2024-03-21 06:42:25', NULL, NULL),
