(1367, '2024-01-23', '1367-1706594696', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '20', 'Asrait', '3', 'Noor Rehman', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3144945022', 'SRSP staff is insisting us to lay down the underground distribution lines. as early as possible because the project is being closed. however, it is not possible for us to do so because the ground is hard due to the absence of rain. therefore we need at least 20 days for installation of distribution lines.', '4', 'the MEAL Manager shared the complaint with Shelter and WASH coordinator for response.', 'Drinking Water Supply Scheme', '4', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abid Rehman', 'Shelter & WASH Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-23', NULL, '2024-01-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'the WASH and Shelter coordinator responded that the \" community can take further time and ensure the distribution of lines within 20 days.\"', 7, '2024-01-30 06:22:41', 7, '2024-01-30 06:28:09', NULL, NULL),
(1368, '2024-01-15', '1368-1706596104', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '21', 'Shinku Bela', '3', 'Atta Ullah', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03469416381', 'I want to request SCI to help us in the water channel in our village. we are facing the water supply issue. we collected some money from the community, but it was not enough. If your organization will help us, we will be very grateful.', '4', 'the request was discussed with MEAL manager for the response.', 'Water Supply Scheme', '3', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Ejaz Shah', 'MEAL Manager', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'it was communicated to the caller that, \"the targetted water supply schemes have been completed. there is no further provision of budget to support any additional intervention.\"', 7, '2024-01-30 06:39:40', NULL, '2024-01-30 06:41:43', NULL, NULL),
(1369, '2024-01-30', '1369-1706597084', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'Bar Alar', '3', 'Javed', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03431011496', 'we have completed the construction work but the contractor did not pay the remuneration to the daily wage laborers engaged during the rehabilitation work at GPS Bar Alar. he did not pick up our call. we want to request you to ask the contractor for early payment.', '1', 'the complaint was initially discussed with the MEAL manager, and he advised to refer the complaint to the partner and communicate the the caller that, \"though it is not SCI nor Partner\'s responsibility to support in the payment of labors engaged by a contractor we will still reach out to contractor by sharing your complaint and earlier response.', 'School rehab', '5', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager (SRSP)', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The Partner responded, \"The matter has been taken up with the contractor and he has made a commitment to clear the dues within the next 4/5 working days. we have also communicated the message to the community as well. \"', 7, '2024-01-30 06:56:41', NULL, '2024-02-06 04:11:30', NULL, NULL),
