(1376, '2024-01-25', '1374-1706600189', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'Behrain', '3', 'Dr. Subhan', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', NULL, 'I recently had the opportunity to visit your commendable free medical camp at village Torwal, organized in collaboration with SRSP. I am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the outstanding efforts and dedication demonstrated by your staff in providing essential healthcare services to the flood-affected population.\r\nI would like to bring to your attention a health concern that I believe requires urgent attention in the Tehsil Bahrain area. Tuberculosis (TB) cases have been notably high, and I humbly request that Save the Children International, in collaboration with SRSP, consider implementing initiatives to address and mitigate the spread of TB in this region. Your organization\'s expertise and commitment to community welfare make you an ideal partner in combatting this health challenge.By extending your support to combat TB, we can collectively contribute to the overall well-being of the community and prevent further transmission of this infectious disease.', '2', 'after discussing the request with MEAL manager, the request forwarded with management for response.', 'Static health facility and mobile health camp', '3', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Rabia Rauf, Irfan Majeed', 'Area Director, MEAL Lead', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The Health & Nutrition Coordinator responded, \"As TB is one of notifiable diseases, the confirmed cases should be notified to the DHO office. However, we don’t have any provisions to confirm the suspected cases, so ideally the patient must refer to the nearby THQ or DHQ where national TB program is in place to confirm the diagnosis through gene Xpert and Sputum culture and further management. \r\nPlease note that TB case management is the only mandate of the TB control program. We can’t even confirm the cases clinically. The suspected case must be immediately referred to combat the spread of the disease.\"', 7, '2024-01-30 07:41:57', NULL, '2024-02-06 04:21:53', NULL, NULL),
(1377, '2024-01-10', '1377-1706600546', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Rasheed Sand', '6', 'Junaid', 'No', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'He said he studies in grade 8. He daily come to the CFS after the school to spend time with his friends. He play with his friends & enjoy alot.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Monitoring visit of CFS', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-01-30 07:46:13', NULL, '2024-01-30 08:38:19', NULL, NULL),
(1378, '2024-01-25', '1378-1706600966', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'Mankar', '3', 'Dr. Muhammad Nazir', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', NULL, 'I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the commendable efforts of DEC.SCI.SRSP in organizing the recent three-day free medical camp in the flood-prone area of Tehsil Bahrain, specifically in Village Mankar.the interesting thing was they displayed the banner on which the hotline was and the email address was given to each individual, they asked if you had any grievances let on this hotline number or email.\r\nHowever, I would like to draw attention to the ongoing struggles faced by the community in the aftermath of the flood. With a significant decline in purchasing power and the disruption of income sources, the need for continued support is paramount. Therefore, I kindly request your organization to consider organizing similar free medical camps in Village Mankar every two or three days.', '2', 'the request was discussed with MEAL Manager KP, and as per his advise it was further shared with partner for response.', 'mobile health camp', '3', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager (SRSP)', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-31', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The Partner responded, \"The MHT has organized a Health camp from 9 to 11 January 2024 in the same village. The team will move to another village in February-2024 so it would not be possible for us to organize another health camp in the village within the project life. we would excuse the request.\"', 7, '2024-01-30 07:52:55', NULL, '2024-02-06 04:13:57', NULL, NULL),
(1379, '2024-01-10', '1378-1706600778', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Rasheed Sand', '6', 'Awais', 'No', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'He said he daily come to the CFS to play & enjoy, he likes the events celebrated here. He told that he also takes part in the activities of the events which he enjoyed alot. Further he told that the facilitators are very polite & friendly with him.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Child Consultation Activity', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-01-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-01-30 07:59:56', NULL, '2024-01-30 08:39:02', NULL, NULL),
(1380, '2023-12-07', '1379-1706601399', 'Zahid Ali Khan', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '19', 'Pardesha', '3', 'Mehreen Rahman', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03437289845', 'As this is my 3rd month in the Camp, I found this camp\'s services result-oriented as it provided services and support to most marginalized people and flood-affected as well. I am working as LHV, and I feel I need someone\'s support as I am managing no serious actions like FP, HCV/HBS Test, Malaria test, HB test, RBS Sugar test, and Rapid Test,  and also do managed clients, secondly, I need Frick that will ease me to take a safe blood sample.', '3', 'the request was forwarded for response.', 'Mobile Health Camp', '4', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Dr. Shahab', 'Manager Health & Nutrition (SRSP)', NULL, '2023-12-07', NULL, '2023-12-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The points of LHV were noted and shared with the health Manager for action. the Frick provision will be ensured after availability at Warehouse.', 7, '2024-01-30 08:03:01', NULL, '2024-01-30 08:05:34', NULL, NULL),
(1381, '2024-01-11', '1380-1706601601', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Meero Kalhoro', '6', 'Sapna', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '0', 'She mentioned that she completed her primary education at the village school. However, she faced a discontinuation in her education journey as there is no middle/high school available in the village. In light of this, she has requested the establishment of a vocational center that can provide training in various skills such as tailoring, beautician, etc.', '3', 'Request for assistance was shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'Children Consultation Activity', '3', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-01-30', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The beneficiary was informed by SCI staff that there is currently no provision for a vocational center within the scope of this project. However, they were assured that any future developments regarding this matter will be communicated accordingly.', 5, '2024-01-30 08:06:41', 8, '2024-02-13 09:07:50', NULL, NULL),
(1382, '2023-12-07', '1381-1706601951', 'Zahid Ali Khan', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '19', 'Pardesha', '3', 'Afshan Bibi', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03325673914', 'Being a psychologist at Camp, I suggest that a separate portion of the PSS sessions need to be managed at MHC to keep the privacy of the client, It is observed that most women clients feel a bit uneasy during individual PFA sessions, as at camp there happened rush and noise of patients, it is observed that fake male patient does visit us but very rare, sometimes polar disorder male client comes at Camp, then being a woman become vigilant, but Camp in charge provided cover, It is requested that learning material should be provided to Camp to engaged clients (mothers comes with younger kids) it will help Psychologist to process relax session with the client.', '3', 'the request forwarded for response.', 'Mobile Health Camp', '4', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager (SRSP)', NULL, '2023-12-07', NULL, '2023-12-07', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The points were valid and shared with the concerned, improvement will be made in the Camp structure and learning material will be provided when available from SCI.', 7, '2024-01-30 08:11:50', NULL, '2024-01-30 08:13:10', NULL, NULL),
