(1394, '2024-01-30', '1394-1706680905', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '168', '14', '95', 'Village janib ujjan  sub village Menhal khan ujjan (GBPS Menhal khan ujjan )', '5', 'Farman Ali', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', NULL, 'I am writing to bring to your attention the case of two beneficiaries in our community, Shahida Khatoon, wife of Asif Ali, and Zubaida, wife of Shoukat Ali. Both individuals have children currently enrolled in school, attending the evening shift where the TLS is also operational. Despite their eligibility, Shahida Khatoon and Zubaida have unfortunately not received financial support from Save the Children, even though their names were included during the validation of forms. This has left them in a state of distress, especially considering that others in similar circumstances have been provided the necessary support. I understand and appreciate the impactful work that Save the Children is doing in our communities, particularly in areas affected by various challenges. On behalf of our community, I express our gratitude for the support you have provided. I kindly request your assistance in reviewing their cases and providing the necessary financial support for their children\'s education through the TLS program.', '2', 'Complain was shared with relevant person for the better understand the situation.', 'TLS', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-31', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Complain was shared with program team, according to them as per the overall referral list, the names of the below beneficiaries are not available. The complainant concerns have been shared with TKF for the future consideration we get any other project.', 8, '2024-01-31 06:26:55', NULL, '2024-02-13 10:25:02', NULL, NULL),
(1395, '2024-01-30', '1395-1706682559', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '38', '91', 'Gul Muhammad Faqeer', '3', 'Iqbal', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03465420034', 'I\'m part of the Village Council at Gull Muhammad Faqeer, and I wanted to share some thoughts with you. Your organization is doing a really great job, especially with the BHU Kolachi project that\'s been super helpful for our community. The free medicines and checkups from BHU Kolachi have been so important for everyone here. The staff is friendly and quick, making our visits really nice. Getting our medicines on time has been a big help, and the support overall has been super important for our health. I just wanted to say a big thank you for everything you\'ve done for us. But I heard that there\'s a chance the organization might close the BHU Kolachi project. That\'s worrying for us because we rely on it. Could you please think again about closing it? We really hope you\'ll keep up the good work in our community.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with focal person.', 'BHU', '1', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Shakeel Patras', 'Senior Coordinator Health & Nutrition', NULL, '2024-01-31', NULL, '2024-02-02', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The positive feedback was disseminated to relevant stakeholder to boost morale and encourage the continuation of successful practices.', 8, '2024-01-31 06:47:00', NULL, '2024-02-02 07:44:15', NULL, NULL),
(1396, '2024-01-30', '1396-1706685716', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '178', '51', '123', 'Peer Bahadur Shah', '10', 'Shah Muhammad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '034004340178', 'I want to convey my heartfelt appreciation to your organization for the support we\'ve received. The kitchen gardening toolkit and the financial assistance for our kitchen gardening activities have had a substantial impact on our well-being, and I am genuinely grateful for this valuable assistance. The toolkit has empowered us to enhance our kitchen gardening efforts, and the financial support has played a crucial role in making our gardening endeavors more effective and sustainable. Thank you so much for making a positive difference in our lives through your generous support.', '1', 'Positive feedback shared with relevant person.', 'Kitchin gardening', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-01-31', NULL, '2024-02-02', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The acknowledgment of positive feedback has been communicated to the relevant individual, encouraging them to persist in their commendable efforts for future endeavors.', 8, '2024-01-31 07:31:04', NULL, '2024-02-02 08:40:25', NULL, NULL);
