(1397, '2024-02-02', '1397-1706855761', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '172', '19', '66', 'Muhammad Sadiquee Bhanojoo', '10', 'Kirshan', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03479991526', 'As the Village Committee member, I want to express our concerns about the pending dues for the construction of two latrines in our village, carried out under your program and NRSP. Currently, there\'s an outstanding amount of around 30 thousand rupees that is yet to be paid to the workers who were involved in the construction. The workers are here in the village, asking for their payment, but we\'re facing difficulties reaching the contractor as our calls are going unanswered. Additionally, the NRSP offices seem to be closed. I kindly ask for your help to get in touch with the person responsible and make sure the workers and co-workers get paid the money they are owed.', '1', 'Complain was shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'WASH', '4', NULL, '6', 'Yes', NULL, 'Fazil Muhammad', 'Senior WASH Coordinator', NULL, '2024-02-02', NULL, '2024-03-19', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'As per the program team, the remaining payment for skilled labor has been disbursed, and they have received their remaining dues. Additionally, they have assured the IP that they will take measures to prevent such hindrances from occurring in the future.', 8, '2024-02-02 06:43:21', NULL, '2024-03-19 05:37:10', NULL, NULL),
(1398, '2024-02-01', '1398-1706856271', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '38', '91', 'Village Bandhhi', '3', 'Shahnawaz', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03073476502', 'I am a resident of Village Bandhi, we are very happy and get benefit from the BHU Kolachi. We came to know that this project is going to be closed soon. We are requesting not to close this project. We don’t have any other health facility like this. We get free medicine from there, and all other health-related issues are being solved by this Health Facility Kindly continue your work with us.', '1', 'Request for assistance was shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'BHU', '3', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Shakeel Patrus', 'Senior Coordinator Health & Nutrition', NULL, '2024-02-02', NULL, '2024-02-13', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Suggestion was shared with senior management team SCI has currently no provision for this request. Community request on rehabilitating health Facility is being considered in the future plans.', 8, '2024-02-02 06:48:23', NULL, '2024-02-13 07:24:08', NULL, NULL),
(1399, '2024-02-06', '1399-1707731368', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Lahskar Khan Cahndio', '6', 'Liqiat', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'I was on my regular visit today in Village Lashkar Khan Chandio, UC Burira District Dadu (EU Project) , it came into my knowledge that 10 days ago a girl (child) got accident with the shelter contractor’s loader vehicle (MAZDA). Her left leg is badly fractured, as per her mother(Hijra) her daughter (Zahira) got operated and due to femur fracture doctor used rod in her leg, and they will go to Larkana after every 02 weeks for further treatment, till complete recovery of fracture. Her mother shared they paid Rs.150,000/- for operation and for other treatment they will be required Rs.14,000/- (Transportation Rs.7500/- Doctor fee Rs.1500/- and Rs.5000/- medicine and other expenses) bi-weekly. During the visit Shelter contractor MMK, and NRSP (IP) staff were present, and it was confirmed from them that incident is not reported yet, and contractor paid Rs.20,000/- to parents.', '5', 'Referred to Datix', 'PDM', '6', '27046', '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sami ullah', 'Head Risk & Compliance', NULL, '2024-02-07', NULL, '2024-05-15', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Case was substantiated & Closed by DATIX handling team', 8, '2024-02-12 10:06:51', NULL, '2024-06-05 06:00:18', NULL, NULL),
(1400, '2024-02-12', '1400-1707815520', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Lashkar Khan Chandio', '6', 'Zulfiqar Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03443395733', 'One of the community members shared “Your organization is constructing shelters in our village; we were bearing 3 times food for 5-6 people (labor) which was not easy for us that we shared with your staff visited our village. Now, instead of food they are asking to pay PKR 1500 per day, which will put the same burden on our shoulders during difficult times, you are requested to look into this matter as well”.', '1', 'Referred to Datix.', 'Shelter Construction', '6', '27108', '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sami Ullah Khan', 'Head Risk & Compliance', NULL, '2024-02-13', NULL, '2024-04-29', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Serious Compliant was reported to DATIX. An independent investigation committee was formed, and they investigated the case. Complaint was substantiated.', 8, '2024-02-13 09:18:07', NULL, '2024-04-29 08:55:27', NULL, NULL),
(1401, '2024-02-12', '1401-1707913125', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '83', 'Village Wali dost bugatii shahi chowki', '5', 'Akbar Bahrani', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03008023945', 'We are deeply grateful for the commendable work your organization is doing. I am delighted to express that the people in my village, who are facing significant economic challenges, have received relief and assistance through your organization. Thank you immensely for your valuable support.', '4', 'Positive response was shred with relevant person.', 'FSL', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-02-14', NULL, '2024-02-15', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Positive feedback has been communicated to the program team to encourage the continuation of excellent work in the future.', 8, '2024-02-14 12:23:47', NULL, '2024-02-15 11:56:05', NULL, NULL),
(1402, '2024-02-15', '1402-1707998198', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Village ladhho dero', '6', 'Arbaab Kahtoon', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03192373833', 'According to the caller, I am in a financially challenging situation, and my house was not included in the shelter program. I am sending you videos and an application for your review. Please assess my current living conditions, as my house is fully damaged, and I am unable to continue living there. I am earnestly requesting you to add my name to the housing scheme. I have heard from my neighbours that your organization provides shelter to people in need, and I would be immensely grateful if you could include my name in the shelter list as well.', '4', 'Request for assistance shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'Shelter construction', '3', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-02-15', NULL, '2024-04-03', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The initial complaint was communicated to the Shelter coordinate. According to him we currently lack sufficient funding to provide carpet coverage and accommodate all selected beneficiaries. Therefore, we were unable to finalize the assessment list for everyone. However, this feedback has been noted for future reference.', 8, '2024-02-15 12:09:12', NULL, '2024-04-03 04:05:45', NULL, NULL),
(1403, '2024-02-19', '1403-1708668381', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '168', '14', '95', 'Muhammad Ishaque Ujjan', '5', 'Mansoor Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03004279231', 'I joined as a facilitator at GBPS Muhammad Ishaque Ujan in October, and unfortunately, my employment was terminated on November 17th. Despite this, I have not received payment for the 17 days I worked before my termination. While I did receive the salary for the month of October, the salary for the remaining 17 days is still pending. I kindly ask for your help to resolve this issue and make sure I receive my remaining salary as soon as possible.', '1', 'Complain was shared with relevant person for the better understanding.', 'TLS', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-02-23', NULL, '2024-04-03', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with the project manager, who informed us that the terminated facilitator had overdue salary for over 10 days. They assured us that the facilitator would receive the salary along with clearance within the week.', 8, '2024-02-23 06:12:57', NULL, '2024-04-03 07:07:14', NULL, NULL),
