(1436, '2024-02-15', '1436-1709277692', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Lahori', '6', 'Hussain Ali', 'No', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'He said that he is very thankful for the cash grant he has been assisted for his livestock. As they are facing lack of fodder for their livestock, it was a great support in shape of cash grant.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'PDM of FSL cash grants', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-02-15', NULL, '2024-02-15', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-03-01 07:31:01', NULL, '2024-03-01 07:31:58', NULL, NULL),
(1437, '2024-02-27', '1437-1709278323', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Meero Kalhoro', '6', 'Murtaza', 'No', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'He said that he feels safe at the CFS due to which he enjoys to come here, his facilitators are very kind & polite to him & take care of him & all the other children who come to the CFS.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback of a child regarding the CFS.', 'Monitoring visit of CFS', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-03-01', NULL, '2024-02-27', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-03-01 07:35:58', NULL, '2024-03-01 07:37:01', NULL, NULL),
(1438, '2024-02-27', '1438-1709278641', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Meero Kalhoro', '6', 'Rabia', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'She said that she likes to come to the CFS because no one scolds her here for playing, she enjoys the games & playing with toys. Facilitators behave very friendly & affectionately with her that\'s why she is very happy.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Monitoring visit of CFS', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-03-01', NULL, '2024-02-27', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is positive feedback of a girl child regarding the CFS.', 5, '2024-03-01 07:44:20', NULL, '2024-03-01 07:45:21', NULL, NULL),
(1439, '2024-02-29', '1439-1709702122', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Burrira', '6', 'Akhtar Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3423776936', 'I am reaching out to you concerning the shelter work currently underway in our village. My house was also selected for this program, and there has been a delay in the construction. My house\'s DPC was completed one and a half months ago, but now, while other village members\' houses are in progress, mine is still pending. The workers are refusing to return and resume work on my house. I have provided them with my tent space to construct my house, and I have moved to my brother\'s house. However, my brother is now refusing to accommodate me. Kindly ask the contractor to restart work on my house so that I can shift back as soon as possible.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person for the better understanding.', 'Shelter Construction', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-03-08', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Complaint was shared with program team to address this issue, according to their response, Despite unforeseen delays caused by material shortages due to heightened construction activity and labor shortages during the election period, we are pleased to inform you that we have successfully overcome these challenges. We are now back on track and anticipate completing all construction activities within the next 1.5 months.', 8, '2024-03-06 05:23:05', 8, '2024-03-08 05:08:22', NULL, NULL),
(1440, '2024-03-05', '1440-1709702679', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Mir Khan Pahi', '6', 'Khadim', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03411869575', 'I am calling you regarding the slow progress in the construction of my house. Currently, we are living under the open sky without proper shelter. The workers do not seem to grasp the seriousness of the matter. My house\'s DPC was completed almost 20 days ago, but since then, no one has come forward to continue the construction. I am worried about the prolonged delay, and I urge you to address this matter urgently.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better address the situation.', 'Shelter Construction', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza  Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-03-08', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'After it received the complaint was shared with the program team to address the issue, and based on their response, despite unexpected delays due to material shortages from increased construction activity and labor shortages during the election. According to their commitment, they will reinforce the workforce to expedite the completion of the remaining work.', 8, '2024-03-06 05:30:36', NULL, '2024-03-08 05:18:04', NULL, NULL),
(1441, '2024-03-04', '1441-1709703040', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Meer Khan Pahi', '6', 'Khadim Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03488349483', 'I am extremely concerned about the delays in the construction of my house. While houses of my fellow villagers are progressing, mine has been stagnant since the completion of the DPC. No one is coming to continue the work, and I am worried about the significant delay. I request your intervention to ensure that someone resumes and completes the construction of my house, just like the progress in other village houses.', '1', 'The complaint was shared with relevant person to better address the complaint.', 'Shelter construction', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-03-08', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'After it received the complaint was shared with the program team to address the issue, and based on their response, despite unexpected delays due to material shortages from increased construction activity and labor shortages during the election. According to their commitment, they will reinforce the workforce to expedite the completion of the remaining work.', 8, '2024-03-06 05:34:39', NULL, '2024-03-08 05:14:38', NULL, NULL);
