(1442, '2024-02-23', '1442-1709705609', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Chibbar Khan Unnar', '6', 'Khadim Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03403512501', 'Initially, my name was chosen for the household assessment of shelter assistance, and I was elated about it. However, later, I discovered that my name did not make it to the final beneficiary list. Unfortunately, my name was also not selected for the government scheme. I am deeply concerned about why my name was excluded from the shelter list.', '1', 'The Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better address the concern.', 'Shelter Construction', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-04-03', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The initial complaint was communicated to the program team. According to the program team, we currently lack sufficient funding to provide carpet coverage and accommodate all selected beneficiaries. Therefore, we were unable to finalize the assessment list for everyone. However, this feedback has been noted for future reference.', 8, '2024-03-06 06:32:05', NULL, '2024-04-03 03:53:06', NULL, NULL),
(1443, '2024-03-04', '1443-1709706730', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Burrira', '6', 'Yakeen Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Non-Beneficiary', '03484040535', 'I am reaching out to you regarding the non-selection of my household in your shelter assistance list. My house was adversely affected by the 2022 flood, and unfortunately, my house was not chosen for the government scheme either. I am deeply concerned and seeking assistance. Kindly consider including my name in your shelter assistance program.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person for better understanding of the concern.', 'Shelter  construction', '4', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-03-05', NULL, '2024-03-25', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint has been forwarded to the program team, who noted that the program lacks carpet coverage for all beneficiaries. We acknowledge this feedback for future reference. Should any refusals arise from the community, we will certainly take such complaints into consideration.', 8, '2024-03-06 06:46:39', NULL, '2024-03-25 07:11:35', NULL, NULL),
(1444, '2024-02-29', '1444-1709712289', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '174', '23', '117', 'Ramzan Babar', '13', 'Mushtaque  Babr', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03209919749', 'I am reaching out to you because I have concerns about the ongoing project in our district, Thatta, specifically related to education over the last few years. I recently learned that your organization has decided to incorporate a vocational center in our village. I am curious about the practice of bringing facilitators from outside our village each time. Our village is home to talented women skilled in handwork and embroidery, yet we locals cannot utilize our space. Additionally, I am worried about the site selection for the vocational center. The chosen site must be reachable and accessible for all girls and females in the community. I am also requesting that if your organization plans to open the vocational center, it should consider engaging local females as trainers for the center.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better address the concern.', 'Vocational', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Farman Khan', 'Senior Program Manager Education/SHN', NULL, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-03-06', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Following the receipt of the complaint, we promptly relayed it to the project team for review according to them, We have carefully addressed the concerns raised regarding our hiring process and the proposed relocation of the ALC. Our hiring decisions were made transparently, with local resources and experts involved to ensure merit-based selections. Regarding the specific complaint, we stand by our decision based on the candidate\'s qualifications and suitability. Regarding the ALC relocation, thorough consultations with stakeholders reveal community opposition due to logistical and familial reasons. We\'ve provided supporting documentation for transparency.', 8, '2024-03-06 08:10:55', NULL, '2024-03-25 06:54:35', NULL, NULL),
(1445, '2024-03-07', '1445-1709875204', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Ali Muhammad Chandio', '6', 'Sohana', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'She said that she enjoys the events celebrated at the CFS such as today they are celebrating women\'s day at the CFS which she is enjoying alot.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Participating in Women\'s day event at CFS Ali Muhammad Chandio', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-03-08', NULL, '2024-03-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-03-08 05:26:44', NULL, '2024-03-08 05:27:44', NULL, NULL),
(1446, '2024-03-07', '1446-1709875670', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Ali Muhammad Chandio', '6', 'Rimsha', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'She said that she comes to the CFS daily to learn embroidery in which she is much interested. Today they are celebrating women\'s day at their CFS in which she is participating in one of the performances.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Participating in Women\'s day event at CFS Ali Muhammad Chandio', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-03-08', NULL, '2024-03-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-03-08 05:32:34', NULL, '2024-03-08 05:33:29', NULL, NULL),
(1447, '2024-03-07', '1447-1709876016', 'Fatima Shahani', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Ali Muhammad Chandio', '6', 'Abdul Ghafoor', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03436022138', 'He said that he visits the CFS daily, he feels very happy here for interacting with his friends & playing with them. Further he told that they have formed a cricket team of CFS with support of their facilitators & play matches which he enjoy\'s alot.', '3', 'It is a positive feedback.', 'Participating in Women\'s day event at CFS Ali Muhammad Chandio', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Nazneen Tabasum', 'CP Coordinator', NULL, '2024-03-08', NULL, '2024-03-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'It is a positive feedback.', 5, '2024-03-08 05:38:25', NULL, '2024-03-08 05:40:01', NULL, NULL),
(1448, '2024-03-08', '1448-1709876869', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '86', 'Muhammad Bux Buggari', '9', 'Muhammad Bux', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03188312842', 'We are delighted with the exceptional work your organization is doing in the field of livestock. Your team is highly commendable, and we recently received valuable training on livestock management and measures to ensure their well-being and protection against various diseases. Thank you very much for the excellent work your organization is carrying out.', '1', 'Positive feedback was shared with relevant person.', 'Livestock training', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-03-08', NULL, '2024-03-19', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Positive feedback has been shared with the relevant personnel regarding their contribution and ongoing dedication to the work.', 8, '2024-03-08 06:15:04', NULL, '2024-03-19 05:44:19', NULL, NULL),
