(1520, '2024-04-01', '1520-1712032235', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '38', '91', 'Kolachi', '3', 'Ghulam Hussain', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'Yes', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03404359534', 'I arrived at the facility with my child to obtain RUTF, but unfortunately, it was unavailable. I have been told on multiple occasions that the RUTF is not in stock. I urgently request that the necessary RUTF be provided as my child\'s health is deteriorating due to its absence.', '1', 'Compalint was shared with the relvant person to better understand the condition.', 'BHU', '4', NULL, '4', 'Yes', NULL, 'Shakeel Patrus', 'Senior Coordinator Health & Nutrition', NULL, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-03', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with the Senior Coordinator of Health & Nutrition, who informed us that the procurement process has been initiated. This process is expected to take approximately one month.', 8, '2024-04-02 04:38:07', NULL, '2024-04-03 04:10:11', NULL, NULL),
(1521, '2024-04-02', '1521-1712032715', 'Saba Saeed', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '19', 'Amlok Bagh', '3', 'Nawab Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03453754109', 'I am a CPC chairman of GPS Amlok Bagh, I along with 1 PTC teacher and 4 CPC members of GPS Amlok Bagh participated in a CPC training session one and a half months ago. However, we have not yet received the per diem amount for the training. We would like to know about the delay in payment.', '1', 'the complaint was initially discussed with MEAL manager KP, further as per MEAL manager\'s advice it was shared with partner for response,', 'CPC refresher training', '4', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Syed Sajjad', 'Project Manager (SRSP)', NULL, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-29', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with project manager SRSP who informed that payment was delayed due to some procedural formalities by the bank. The inconvenience is regretted. However, the training participants will receive their perdiam payment in next 10 days. Later it was confirmed by the partner staff that the payment is received by the training participants, and they were satisfied. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner.', 7, '2024-04-02 04:44:01', NULL, '2024-05-07 12:28:25', NULL, NULL),
(1522, '2024-03-20', '1521-1712032881', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '86', 'Khameesa Khan Village', '5', 'Ahmad Ali', 'Yes', 'Boy', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03417742803', 'I am grateful for the presence of TKF in our village and for the educational sessions conducted by your organization\'s team. They provided us with valuable lessons on understanding good touch and bad touch, as well as information about VENA. I want to express my sincere appreciation to your organization for these efforts.', '1', 'Positive feedback has been shared with project manager.', 'CP', '1', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-02', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The concerned individual received positive feedback, aimed at motivating them to uphold their dedication and enthusiasm in their work.', 8, '2024-04-02 04:49:40', NULL, '2024-04-02 08:30:27', NULL, NULL),
(1523, '2024-04-01', '1523-1712033443', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '41', 'Jurio Halio', '6', 'Farzana Ayaz Ali', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03483961034', 'I am a widow with eight children, struggling to survive after my house was damaged in the 2022 flood, resulting in the loss of my livestock as well. Although initially selected for your kitchen gardening assistance my name was omitted from the final list. I urgently request reconsideration for inclusion in the kitchen gardening program, as I am in dire need.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better address the concern.', 'KG', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Ali Aman shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-26', 'Partially Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with the program team, and according to their response, the complaint data was not found in the overall database. Consequently, that beneficiary was not selected for the initial assessment phase. Due to budget constraints, we were unable to accommodate all beneficiaries, and thus there is no coverage for them at this time.', 8, '2024-04-02 05:14:03', NULL, '2024-04-26 06:52:54', NULL, NULL),
