(1525, '2024-04-02', '1525-1712039226', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '86', 'Madadpur', '5', 'Roshan Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03453977185', 'I am teacher at P.S. Madadpur, your organization has initiated rehabilitation work at our school. I have concerns regarding the ongoing rehabilitation work. Specifically, the boundary wall\'s height does not meet proper standards. Additionally, the same damaged doors are being used for classrooms, which are in poor condition and not suitable for use.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better understand the concern.', 'Education', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The concern was conveyed to the program team, and based on their response, the initial budget was primarily allocated for rehabilitating the school\'s infrastructure according to the BOQs.  However, due to the extensive area of the school, which comprises a lengthy boundary wall and approximately 12 to 13 rooms, it was not feasible to construct the wall to its maximum length within the budget constraints.', 8, '2024-04-02 06:31:29', NULL, '2024-04-24 05:32:35', NULL, NULL),
