(1547, '2024-04-16', '1547-1713517273', 'Abdul Qadeer', 'Close', '4', '168', '14', '95', 'Darya Khan Shanbani', '5', 'Rizwan', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '3068048605', 'Our community is thrilled and wants to express our sincere gratitude for the educational support given to our children. Since receiving the school bags and hygiene kits, our kids are happily heading to school with excitement and smiles. Your kindness has made a big difference in their education and happiness, and we are deeply thankful.', '3', 'Thank you, message has been, shared with staff member.', 'Field Monitoring Visit', '1', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abdur, Razzaq', 'Education Coordinator', NULL, '2024-04-17', NULL, '2024-04-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The positive response has been conveyed to the program team, and they are appreciated for their ongoing and future contributions to the project.', 15, '2024-04-19 09:07:30', 8, '2024-04-24 06:01:51', NULL, NULL),
