(1549, '2024-04-18', '1549-1713518474', 'Abdul Qadeer', 'Close', '4', '168', '54', '127', 'Buxan Khan Noonari', '5', 'Parveen', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '237292593', 'From the training sessions, we\'ve gained valuable insights and learned effective practices for kitchen gardening along with essential tools. We sincerely appreciate you for organizing such beneficial training sessions. Thank you for providing us with this opportunity to enhance our knowledge and skills.', '3', 'Thank you, message has been, shared with staff member.', 'Field Monitoring visit', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman Shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-04-18', NULL, '2024-04-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The positive response has been conveyed to the program team, and they are appreciated for their ongoing and future contributions to the project.', 15, '2024-04-19 09:28:11', 8, '2024-04-24 06:22:20', NULL, NULL),
(1550, '2024-04-01', '1550-1713783688', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '4', '100', '9', '90', 'Village Lashkar khan chandio', '6', 'Inayat Ali', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03483177329', 'As a resident of village Lashkar Khan Chandio, my house was selected by your organization for shelter construction. The NRSP team has commenced work on constructing shelters and toilets in our village. However, it has come to our attention that the toilets, which have now begun construction, are positioned in a manner that their directions is towards the Qibla. This is deeply concerning to us, as it goes against our religious beliefs, and we cannot accept and use toilets constructed in such a manner.', '1', 'Complaint was shared with the relevant person to better understand the concern.', 'Shelter', '5', NULL, '5', 'Yes', NULL, 'Raza Khan', 'Shelter & Construction Coordinator - Sindh', NULL, '2024-04-01', NULL, '2024-04-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'As per the shelter coordinator, the toilets have been demolished and reconstructed to meet the community\'s demands and to prevent any future structures that may conflict with community standards and beliefs.', 8, '2024-04-22 11:17:56', NULL, '2024-04-24 05:07:43', NULL, NULL),
(1551, '2024-04-18', '1551-1713945350', 'Abdul Qadeer', 'Close', '4', '168', '54', '127', 'Buxan Khan Noonari', '49', 'farzna', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '3003101938', 'We\'re thrilled to have received the seeds for kitchen gardening following the informative training session. The demonstration taught us valuable practices, and we\'re grateful for your support during this challenging time. Thank you!', '3', 'Community positive response and message has been shared with program team.', 'KG trainng filed monitoring', '1', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliaman,shah', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-04-19', NULL, '2024-04-24', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The positive response has been conveyed to the program team, and they are appreciated for their ongoing and future contributions to the project.', 15, '2024-04-24 08:08:53', 8, '2024-04-24 11:39:29', NULL, NULL),
