(1562, '2024-04-19', '1562-1714031077', 'Shazia Gull', 'Close', '3', '178', '34', '86', 'NFE Ghous Bux Golo', '5', 'Wahida', 'No', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', NULL, 'I want to extend my gratitude to your organization, save the children and TKF for its commendable work in our community. The team has been helpful, providing us with valuable knowledge. We received school bags and stationary items, which have been incredibly beneficial. Personally, I am overjoyed because, before TLS opened, I never attended school and only assisted my mother with household chores. However, since enrolling at NFE, I am now receiving an education. I am immensely thankful to your organization for this opportunity. Currently, I am a fifth-grade student.request to extend the project duration.', '3', 'Request for assistance shared with Relevant person for the better understanding.', 'Monitoring visit of TLs', '3', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Abdur Razzaq Malik', 'Education Coordinator', NULL, '2024-04-25', NULL, '2024-04-26', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The project has already been granted a two-month extension by the program team due to budget constraints. Unfortunately, we are unable to extend the project duration further. However, please know that your positive feedback has been taken into consideration.', 14, '2024-04-25 07:48:41', NULL, '2024-04-26 04:38:23', NULL, NULL),
(1563, '2024-04-24', '1563-1714109389', 'Shahida Khaskheli', 'Close', '3', '176', '33', '83', 'Hajji Abdul Razzaq Umrani', '5', 'Murada', 'Yes', 'Girl', 'Less than 18 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03426094684', 'I am a fourth-grade student at TLS Haji Razzaq Umrani. Previously, we were very happy with the teaching provided by TLS teachers. However, recently, the TLS teachers have stopped coming regularly, and the government teacher only visits once a week. Additionally, the government teacher does not dedicate as much time to us as the TLS teachers did. We kindly request that TLS teachers be reinstated so that we can continue learning effectively from them.', '1', 'Request for assistance was shared with the program team to better understand the concern.', 'TLS', '3', NULL, '1', 'Yes', NULL, 'Kehkishan Rani', 'Project Manager', NULL, '2024-04-26', NULL, '2024-05-10', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Compliant was shared with respective project manager. According to PM ECHO \"NFE component has ended and children has been transferred to regular schooling. Contracts of teachers (NFE Facilitators) were also ended therefore, they are not coming to TLCs anymore\" Sector response was communicated back to caller.', 8, '2024-04-26 05:35:11', NULL, '2024-06-05 07:10:00', NULL, NULL),
(1564, '2024-04-18', '1564-1714391606', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'Koza Gheri Khawar, Sataal', '9', 'Muhammad Nawaz', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03109518461', 'I would like to inform you that we (Muhammad Nawaz, Muhammad Ibrahim and Muhammad Riaz) have worked on CFW irrigation water channel at Koza Gheri Khwar but we did not receive our wages. Kindly let us know when we will receive the payment.', '1', 'The project manager SRSP informed on same day that due to some CNIC validation error, the payment was delayed through HBL but as on 24/04/2024 the complainants have received the payment. Later it was verified from the complainant and the complaint was closed.', 'CFW Scheme - Irrigation water channel', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayyed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-04-24', NULL, '2024-04-29', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP. It was informed by SRSP that due to problem with CNIC data of some beneficiaries the whole batch of transaction was delayed by HBL Konnect. The revised data of CNICs was shared with the bank and the payment was received by all CFW beneficiaries except two. Later it was confirmed by MEAL team from the complainant that they have received the cash and were satisfied.', 4, '2024-04-29 12:27:19', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:37:16', NULL, NULL),
(1565, '2024-04-18', '1565-1714393662', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '28', 'Sotarbagh', '9', 'Ali Jan and Adil Bakht', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03442471210', 'I want to inform you that we (Ali Jan and Adil Bakht) have not received our wages even after 2 months of water channel construction completion. We request you to kindly let us know when the payment will be transferred to us.', '1', 'It was telephonically informed by project manager SRSP that all CFW beneficiaries will receive their pending payment before 25th April 2024. There were some CNIC issues, so the bank held all the transfers unless data issues are resolved for the full batch of transaction.', 'CFW Scheme', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-04-18', NULL, '2024-04-26', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The SRSP Staff informed that the payment was delayed due to CNIC data of some beneficiaries due to which the bank delayed the batch transaction. However, on 24/04/2024 the payment has been received by all complainants. Later it was confirmed by MEAL team that the complainants have received their wage payment before 27th Apr 2024. The complaint was closed.', 4, '2024-04-29 12:44:20', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:41:08', NULL, NULL),
(1566, '2024-04-18', '1566-1714394664', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '28', 'Sotarbagh', '9', 'Noman Khalid', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03449753832', 'I have worked on CFW Scheme irrigation water channel at village Sotarbagh but I have not received the payment on account of daily wages. Kindly update about the expected payment receiving date. It has been more than 2 months that I could not receive the payment despite submitting all relevant documents.', '1', 'It was telephonically informed by project manager SRSP that payment will be transferred before 25th of April 2024. There were CNIC issues of some of the beneficiaries therefore the bank did not transfer the payment to the entire batch. The inconvenience is regretted.', 'CFW Scheme', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayyed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-04-18', NULL, '2024-04-26', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'SRSP staff informed that payment was delayed due to some CNIC data error of some beneficiaries. Therefore, the bank delayed the batch transaction. Later it was confirmed by the complainant that he received the payment on 25th April 2024. The complaint was closed.', 4, '2024-04-29 12:52:18', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:44:03', NULL, NULL),
(1567, '2024-04-25', '1567-1714447946', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '6', '26', 'Dad Tarogay', '3', 'Amin ul Haq', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03453670039', 'I am chairman PTC at GPS Dad Toragay. I want to know when will you provide the books to the children.', '1', 'It was informed by education coordinator KP that Save the Children will provide school bags and stationary items to the children, but books are only provided by government. The parents should contact the school administration for provision of books.', 'School Rehab work', '2', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Farhat Riaz', 'Education Coordinator KP', NULL, '2024-04-29', NULL, '2024-04-30', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complainant was told that SRSP/SCI do not provide books to any school, rather the books are provided by government. Therefore, he was advised to contact the government education department or school administration to get the books for the children. The complaint was closed after consultation with SRSP staff\'s feedback. The response was communicated to the caller and he was satisfied.', 4, '2024-04-30 03:40:44', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:47:30', NULL, NULL),
(1568, '2024-04-17', '1568-1714448479', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '94', 'GGPS Ushoo', '9', 'Fazal', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03135004166', 'I want to inform you that rehab work is incomplete and there is no construction work worker at the school. The quality of construction work is also very poor.', '1', 'The project manager SRSP informed that construction work is delayed due to rain and limited access due to land sliding. The matter was discussed with the contractor, and it will be ensured that work is completed in May 2024 and quality of work will be reviewed by field engineer.', 'School Rehab Work', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayyed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-04-17', NULL, '2024-05-06', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP. He informed that rehab work was delayed due to rainfall and limited road access due to land sliding. However, the contractor has been asked to expedite the work. The rehab work will be completed before 20th May 2024 and quality of work will be reviewed by SCI and SRSP field engineer. The response was communicated by MEAL team to the caller, and he was satisfied. In case the rehab work is not completed by 20th May 2024 then complainant was requested to lodge the complaint again.', 4, '2024-04-30 03:55:55', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:52:54', NULL, NULL),
(1569, '2024-04-17', '1569-1714449360', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '5', '24', 'GPS Ossar', '3', 'Tariq Aziz', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Indirect Beneficiary', '03465649266', 'School rehab work is incomplete at GPS Osaar. There is water leakage from the roof of newly constructed classroom. The Water supply pipeline is also not initiated due to unavailability of technical field engineer.', '1', 'It was informed by Project Manager SRSP that work was delayed due to rainfall. I will send the field engineer and SO to GPS Ossar to review the status. All rectification work will be completed. Regarding water supply, we have already provided the pipes to the school administration and they have to initiate the work which will be facilitated by our field engineer.', 'School Rehab Work', '4', NULL, '2', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayyed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-04-17', NULL, '2024-05-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'The complaint was shared with Project Manager SRSP and SCI field engineer. The SRSP staff informed that all the rectification work as per BOQs will be completed before 20th May 2024. The work was delayed due to bad weather. The roof leakage will be resolved. The water supply scheme has been initiated by the community with the technical support of SRSP field engineer. The complaint was closed after receiving satisfactory response from SRSP. The site will also be inspected by SCI Field Engineer.', 4, '2024-04-30 04:06:37', NULL, '2024-05-07 11:58:35', NULL, NULL),
