(1583, '2024-05-07', '1583-1715063658', 'Ejaz Shah', 'Close', '2', '49', '4', '29', 'Morepandai, Teraat', '9', 'MS Umama Zeeshan', 'Yes', 'Female', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03424440428', 'I received Kitchen Gardening Toolkit but not received cash. There was error in CNIC number written by SRSP. SRSP staff made correction of my CNIC but still I did not get the cash. Kindly let me know when you will transfer cash.', '1', 'The complaint shared with project manager SRSP. Who responded that there were some CNIC data errors of 33 beneficiaries. The corrections were made and revised data is shared with the bank for further action. Hopefully, all remaining beneficiaries will receive the cash within next 7 days. The beneficiary was informed accordingly, and she was satisfied.', 'FSL CCG', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Sayyed Sajjad', 'Project Manager SRSP', NULL, '2024-05-07', NULL, '2024-05-07', 'Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'Project Manager SRSP responded that due to some CNIC data error around 33 beneficiaries could not timely receive the cash. The inconvenience is regretted. However, we have completed the cancelation procedure and shared the revised list with the bank for payment. The bank takes at least 5-6 days to process the payment. Therefore all 33 beneficiaries will receive their payment well before 20th May 2024. The complaint was closed after satisfactory action taken by the partner and same response was communicated to the complainant.', 4, '2024-05-07 06:49:33', NULL, '2024-05-08 03:48:50', NULL, NULL),
