(1705, '2024-06-13', '1705-1718347187', 'Rehana Khan', 'Close', '4', '168', '35', '48', 'Moula', '3', 'Ghulam Muhammad', 'Yes', 'Male', '19-50 years', 'No', 'Direct Beneficiary', '03008964686', 'According to complainant: \" A team came to livestock assessment in our area. Survey team did not go to door-to-door household level assessment. While the field team all assessment forms filled of favorited peoples in the Otaq of Azad Burhan”.It is requested to you that our 10 families should also be include in assessment. We will be thank full to you.', '1', 'Complaint sent to respective department for further process.', 'livestock & agriculture beneficiary assessment', '4', NULL, '3', 'Yes', NULL, 'Aliman', 'FSL Manager', NULL, '2024-06-13', NULL, '2024-07-09', 'Not Satisfied', NULL, NULL, 'As per accountability officer khairpur field investigation report.\r\nVillage: Ghulam Muhammad, Out of the total 250 households, over 120 were assessed, but when I made a random field visit to the village and physically verified 3 households, it was found that the assessment was carried out by the field team side household level.\r\nComplaint closed after sharing report information with complainant.', 103, '2024-06-14 07:03:14', NULL, '2024-07-31 11:20:53', NULL, NULL),
